Homeland chain needs to be changed anywa.key: Homeland chain needs to be changed anyway

TBD could become Monte Castello for a ti.key: TBD could become Monte Castello for a tilean fortress landmark, Argalis was supposed to be a port

agent_actions_localised_action_descripti.value_original: [[col:yellow]]Grants %n experience per turn to units serving in the parent army.[[/col]]
agent_actions_localised_action_descripti.value_translated: [[col:yellow]]Otorga %n de experiencia por turno a las unidades que sirven en el ejército padre.[[/col]]

agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_original: Duellists and Dietros will fight anybody for the right price, favour or well, any reason they may think of.\\nBuy a contract in the Plutocracy panel to improve Master Duellist recruitment.
agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_translated: Los duelistas y dietros lucharán contra cualquiera por el precio justo, un favor o, bueno, cualquier razón que se les ocurra.\nCompra un contrato en el panel Plutocracia para mejorar la contratación de Maestros duelistas.

agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_original: Captains have risen through the ranks, having first stood amongst the rank and file with a bloody sword in their hands.
agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_translated: Los capitanes han ascendido a través de las filas, habiendo estado primero entre los soldados rasos con una espada ensangrentada en sus manos.

agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_original: By prayer, training and tactics, the templars of Myrmidia will strive to crush the unholy and the unclean.
agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_translated: Mediante la oración, el entrenamiento y la táctica, los templarios de Myrmidia se esforzarán por aplastar a los impíos e impuros.

agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_original: Away from institutional colleges and watery cults, generals have to make do by hiring hedge wizards that look moderately reliable.\\nBuy a contract in the Plutocracy panel to hire wizards.
agent_subtype_subculture_overrides_descr.value_translated: Lejos de los colegios institucionales y los cultos acuosos, los generales tienen que apañárselas contratando hechiceros de cobertura que parezcan medianamente fiables.\NCompra un contrato en el panel Plutocracia para contratar magos.

agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_original: Duellists, also known as Diestros in Estalia, are agents, swashbucklers and rascals who'd produce their rapiers at the drop of a penny. Among the best of them, swordsmanship is as legendary as their boasts!
agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_translated: Los duelistas, también conocidos como Diestros en Estalia, son agentes, espadachines y granujas que sacarían sus estoques a la primera de cambio. Entre los mejores, su habilidad con la espada es tan legendaria como sus fanfarronadas.

agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_original: Mercenary captains are usually found leading companies of local troops or mercenaries, generally trying to make sure they get paid and not maimed too much.
agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_translated: Los capitanes mercenarios suelen estar al mando de compañías de tropas locales o mercenarios, y generalmente intentan asegurarse de que les pagan y no les mutilan demasiado.

agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_original: Mercenary generals are powerful individuals of various origins, from Princes to former soldiers, with the wealth and usually the know-how to employ armies of militias and mercenaries.
agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_translated: Los generales mercenarios son poderosos individuos de diversos orígenes, desde príncipes a antiguos soldados, con la riqueza y normalmente los conocimientos necesarios para emplear ejércitos de milicias y mercenarios.

agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_original: Priestesses and Knights at once, the high-ranking officers of the Order of the Eagle are expert fighters and unrivalled tacticians.
agent_subtypes_description_text_override.value_translated: Sacerdotisas y Caballeras a la vez, las oficiales de alto rango de la Orden del Águila son expertas luchadoras y tácticas sin rival.

agent_subtypes_onscreen_name_override_te.value_original: [this is a dummy that only exists for frontend bundle effect shenanigans]
agent_subtypes_onscreen_name_override_te.value_translated: [this is a dummy that only exists for frontend bundle effect shenanigans]

agent_subtypes_onscreen_name_override_te.value_translated: [this is a dummy that only exists for frontend bundle effect shenanigans]

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_bor_ranger.value_original: A horse can outrun Orcs, Trolls, even Giants. Not arrows. Or Doom Divers. But it still helps.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_bor_ranger.value_translated: Un caballo puede dejar atrás Orcos, Trolls, incluso Gigantes. No flechas. O Lanzagoblinz. Pero aún así ayuda.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_bor_ranger.value_original: Persuading a Warboss to flee is much easier with a repeater rifle from the Empire. Expensive, but worth it.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_bor_ranger.value_translated: Persuadir a un Jefe de Guerra para que huya es mucho más fácil con un rifle de repetición del Imperio. Caro, pero merece la pena.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_est_inquis.value_original: A flying monster from the northern ridges, a Hippogryph makes for a loyal and protective mount when trained.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_est_inquis.value_translated: El Hipogrifo, un monstruo volador de las cordilleras del norte, es una montura leal y protectora cuando está entrenado.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_est_inquis.value_original: Horse plate bardings are expensive, but might stop the heathen or monster from killing your mount outright.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_est_inquis.value_translated: Los bardos con placas de caballo son caros, pero pueden evitar que un pagano o un monstruo mate a tu montura.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_est_inquis.value_original: A good warhorse is not only a symbol of authority, also a swift vehicle that can bite and kick the enemy.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_est_inquis.value_translated: Un buen caballo de guerra no sólo es un símbolo de autoridad, sino también un vehículo veloz que puede morder y patear al enemigo.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_borgio.value_original: Can't be properly imposing without a plated barding for the horse.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_borgio.value_translated: No se puede imponer adecuadamente sin una armadura chapada para el caballo.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_borgio.value_original: A horse can outrun Orcs, Trolls, even Giants. Not arrows. Or Doom Divers. But it still helps.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_borgio.value_translated: Un caballo puede dejar atrás Orcos, Trolls, incluso Gigantes. No flechas. O Doom Divers. Pero aún así ayuda.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_cadavo.value_original: Cadavo's current steed is an ill-tempered gelding only loyal and tending to Cadavo. To those few he doesn't kick on sight, he answers to the name of Broccolo.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_cadavo.value_translated: El actual corcel de Cadavo es un castrado malhumorado que sólo es leal a Cadavo. A los pocos que no patea en cuanto lo ven, responde al nombre de Broccolo.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_cadavo.value_original: Cadavo's current steed is an ill-tempered gelding only loyal and tending to Cadavo. To those few he doesn't kick on sight, he answers to the name of Broccolo.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_cadavo.value_translated: El actual corcel de Cadavo es un castrado malhumorado que sólo es leal y cariñoso con Cadavo. A los pocos que no patea nada más verlo, responde al nombre de Brócolo.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_catraz.value_original: Good metal barding is important against foes that can otherwise cleave your horse in twain in one blow.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_catraz.value_translated: Una buena armadura metálica es importante contra enemigos que pueden partir tu caballo en dos de un solo golpe.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_catraz.value_original: A horse can outrun Orcs, Trolls, even Giants. Not arrows. Or Doom Divers. But it still helps.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_catraz.value_translated: Un caballo puede dejar atrás a Orcos, Trolls e incluso Gigantes. No flechas. O Doom Divers. Pero aún así ayuda.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_colomb.value_original: "This baby can do zero to fifty in nothing! And I swear she can understand everything I- did she just write "sixty" with her hoof?"
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_colomb.value_translated: "¡Este bebé puede hacer de cero a cincuenta en nada! Y te juro que entiende todo lo que yo... ¿Acaba de escribir "sesenta" con la pezuña?".

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_colomb.value_original: A lucky prey from a skirmish against Corsairs, this rare magical repeater crossbow is too cumbersome for use on foot, but if you want something positively dead, it's a nice toy. Just have to hope the magic in it isn't too dark.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_colomb.value_translated: Una presa afortunada de una escaramuza contra Corsarios, esta rara ballesta mágica de repetición es demasiado engorrosa para usarla a pie, pero si quieres algo positivamente muerto, es un bonito juguete. Solo tienes que esperar que la magia que contiene no sea demasiado oscura.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_gausse.value_original: Good metal barding is important against foes that can otherwise cleave your horse in twain in one blow.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_gausse.value_translated: Una buena armadura metálica es importante contra enemigos que pueden partir tu caballo en dos de un solo golpe.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_gausse.value_original: A rare arabyan Pegasus, gifted by Crusaders. A living and swift siphon of light and magic, ready to unleash their energy on aggressors.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_gausse.value_translated: Un raro pegaso árabe, regalado por los cruzados. Un sifón vivo y veloz de luz y magia, listo para desatar su energía sobre los agresores.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_gausse.value_original: A horse can outrun Orcs, Trolls, even Giants. Not arrows. Or Doom Divers. But it still helps.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_gausse.value_translated: Un caballo puede dejar atrás a orcos, trolls e incluso gigantes. No flechas. O Buzos del Destino. Pero aún así ayuda.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lucrez.value_original: A proper Bretonnian steed, fast and with fine cloth barding. None of that spiky steely business.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lucrez.value_translated: Un auténtico corcel bretoniano, rápido y con una fina armadura de tela. Nada de ese asunto del acero puntiagudo.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lucrez.value_original: A horse can outrun Orcs, Trolls, even Giants. Not arrows. Or Doom Divers. But it still helps.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lucrez.value_translated: Un caballo puede dejar atrás a Orcos, Trolls e incluso Gigantes. No flechas. O Lanzagoblinz. Pero aún así ayuda.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lupio_.value_original: "I had actually sent to buy a unicorn. Made of diamonds. Like, a real live unicorn made of diamonds, very stylish. But they say it can't be done. Unimaginative buggers, the lot of them."
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lupio_.value_translated: "En realidad había enviado a comprar un unicornio. Hecho de diamantes. Como, un unicornio de verdad hecho de diamantes, muy elegante. Pero dicen que no se puede hacer. Son unos cabrones sin imaginación".

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lupio_.value_original: Lupio's own demigryph owes his companionship to Lupio and "Big Magpie" nickname to his distinctive black and white coat and attraction towards shiny baubles.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lupio_.value_translated: El semigrifo de Lupio debe su compañerismo a Lupio y su apodo de "Gran Urraca" a su característico pelaje blanco y negro y a su atracción por las chucherías brillantes.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lupio_.value_original: A horse can outrun Orcs, Trolls, even Giants. Not arrows. Or Doom Divers. But it still helps.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_lupio_.value_translated: Un caballo puede dejar atrás Orcos, Trolls, incluso Gigantes. No flechas. O Doom Divers. Pero aún así ayuda.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_priest.value_original: Horse plate bardings are expensive, but might stop the heathen or monster from killing your mount outright.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_priest.value_translated: Los bardajes para el caballo son caros, pero pueden evitar que el pagano o el monstruo mate a tu montura directamente.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_priest.value_original: A good warhorse is not only a symbol of authority, also a swift vehicle that can bite and kick the enemy.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_priest.value_translated: Un buen caballo de guerra no es sólo un símbolo de autoridad, sino también un vehículo veloz que puede morder y patear al enemigo.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_original: An excellent steed barded in stylish burnished steel, for the man that must not ask "Eh?".
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_translated: Un excelente corcel bardado en elegante acero bruñido, para el hombre que no debe preguntar "¿Eh?".

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_original: Behind the erudite mask of this Myrmidian commander lies the untamed spirit of a warrior. In battle, his arms glare of such a violent and supernatural light that even the untainted cannot stare for long.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_translated: Tras la máscara erudita de este comandante mirmidiano se esconde el espíritu indomable de un guerrero. En la batalla, sus brazos brillan con una luz tan violenta y sobrenatural que ni siquiera los impolutos pueden mirar durante mucho tiempo.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_original: An exotic beast, the demigryph, mighty dangerous too. Whoever intends to tame and befriend one must be strong of will and limb, because even the best suits of plate are not demigryph-proof.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_translated: El semigrifo es una bestia exótica y muy peligrosa. Quien pretenda domarla y entablar amistad con ella debe ser fuerte de voluntad y de miembros, porque ni los mejores trajes de placas son a prueba de semigrifos.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_original: Fly on your wings, fly, and touch the sun.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_teb_templa.value_translated: Vuela con tus alas, vuela y toca el sol.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_til_mercha.value_original: Horse plate bardings are expensive, but might stop the heathen or monster from killing your mount outright.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_til_mercha.value_translated: Los caballos de guerra bardados son caros, pero pueden evitar que el pagano o el monstruo mate a tu montura directamente.

ancillaries_colour_text_mount_til_mercha.value_original: A good warhorse is not only a symbol of authority, also a swift vehicle that can bite and kick the enemy.
ancillaries_colour_text_mount_til_mercha.value_translated: Un buen caballo de guerra no sólo es un símbolo de autoridad, también es un vehículo veloz que puede morder y patear al enemigo.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_borgio_armou.value_original: Only some scholars might know what those statues were about, but once melted and used to forge this huge brazen armour, they might have brought over whatever enchantment they used to bear...
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_borgio_armou.value_translated: Sólo algunos eruditos sabrán de qué eran esas estatuas, pero una vez fundidas y utilizadas para forjar esta enorme armadura de bronce, podrían haber traído consigo cualquier encantamiento que llevaran...

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_borgio_mace.value_original: During the Siege of Remas, a cannonball flew straight at Borgio. Instead of rather influential smithereens, bystanders witnessed that the projectile was stuck right into the Prince's armour, who was barely wounded. Melted and reshaped as a mace, the cannonball makes for a terrifying and symbolic weapon.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_borgio_mace.value_translated: Durante el asedio de Remas, una bala de cañón voló directamente hacia Borgio. En lugar de hacerse añicos, los espectadores fueron testigos de que el proyectil se clavó justo en la armadura del príncipe, que apenas resultó herido. Fundida y remodelada como maza, la bala de cañón constituye un arma aterradora y simbólica.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_borgio_mask.value_original: During the most furious melees, Borgio wears his frightening mask, a grotesque grimace of malice. Coupled with the wearer's bulk and might, the effect is scary indeed.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_borgio_mask.value_translated: Durante los combates más furiosos, Borgio lleva su aterradora máscara, una grotesca mueca de malicia. Junto con el volumen y la fuerza de su portador, el efecto es realmente aterrador.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_cadavo_talis.value_original: An amulet made of a weird alloy, capable of neutralizing poisons and many of the magical properties for weapons that would injure the bearer.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_cadavo_talis.value_translated: Un amuleto hecho de una extraña aleación, capaz de neutralizar venenos y muchas de las propiedades mágicas de las armas que podrían herir al portador.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_catrazza_rin.value_original: Catrazza is not usually one for religious displays, but there are solid practical and diplomatical advantages for wearing this ring around.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_catrazza_rin.value_translated: A Catrazza no le suelen gustar las exhibiciones religiosas, pero llevar este anillo tiene sólidas ventajas prácticas y diplomáticas.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_catrazza_swo.value_original: An ancient elven blade, relic of a time when Tilea was an Asur colony. Its wielder's attacks leave a glowing and elegant trail of light and molten armour.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_catrazza_swo.value_translated: Una antigua espada élfica, reliquia de una época en la que Tilea era una colonia Asur. Los ataques de su portador dejan un rastro brillante y elegante de luz y armadura fundida.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_colombo_gem.value_original: A reward from the Slann, this amulet in the shape of Sotek's tongue feels oddly alive and protected the wearer more times than he recalls.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_colombo_gem.value_translated: Recompensa del Slann, este amuleto con forma de lengua de Sotek se siente extrañamente vivo y ha protegido a su portador más veces de las que recuerda.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_colombo_scro.value_original: Used by someone to write an otherwise uninteresting map, this scroll bears potent enchantments of Nehekharan protective magic. However, it tends to crumble a bit with each use.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_colombo_scro.value_translated: Utilizado por alguien para escribir un mapa que, por lo demás, carece de interés, este pergamino contiene potentes encantamientos de magia protectora nehekhariana. Sin embargo, tiende a desmoronarse un poco con cada uso.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_duellist_her.value_original: Duellists are usually more comfortable fighting on solid ground rather than on a snorting beast, but they are also adaptable people at heart.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_duellist_her.value_translated: Los duelistas suelen sentirse más cómodos luchando en tierra firme que sobre una bestia bufadora, pero también son personas adaptables en el fondo.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_duellist_her.value_original: The customary uniform of the Knights Encarmine involves full plate, two swords, red paint and an unhealthy quantity of sass.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_duellist_her.value_translated: El uniforme habitual de los Caballeros Encarminados consiste en una armadura completa, dos espadas, pintura roja y una cantidad insana de descaro.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_duellist_her.value_original: Duellists are usually more comfortable fighting on solid ground rather than on a snorting beast, but they are also adaptable people at heart.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_duellist_her.value_translated: Los duelistas suelen sentirse más cómodos luchando en tierra firme que sobre una bestia resoplando, pero también son personas adaptables en el fondo.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_eldaddio_arm.value_original: The best smiths were called to restore Eustaquio's plate armour. However, he wouldn't let anyone replace the chest piece or repair the hole through which the Nehekharans ripped out his heart.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_eldaddio_arm.value_translated: Se llamó a los mejores herreros para restaurar la armadura de placas de Eustaquio. Sin embargo, Eustaquio no dejó que nadie le cambiara la pieza del pecho ni reparara el agujero por el que los nehekharanos le arrancaron el corazón.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_eldaddio_wea.value_original: The weapon is an old gift from the Black Guard to the then-High Eagle of Myrmidia, and later made its way to Eustaquio. It is excruciatingly sharp and smells faintly of rotting roses. No matter what, Eustaquio seems to be viciously gripping it like a life-line.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_eldaddio_wea.value_translated: El arma es un antiguo regalo de la Guardia Negra a la entonces Alta Águila de Myrmidia, y más tarde llegó a Eustaquio. Es insoportablemente afilada y huele ligeramente a rosas podridas. Pase lo que pase, Eustaquio parece agarrarla con saña como si fuera un salvavidas.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gashnag_book.value_original: Knowledge is power, and this learning comes from the Strigoi patriarch's secrets and mistakes.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gashnag_book.value_translated: Aprender de los secretos y errores del patriarca de los Strigoi podría no tener precio.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gashnag_staf.value_original: One of Ushoran's own artefacts, this polestaff supposedly allowed the original Strigoi patriarch to hold off the Lahmians' aggression for so long.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gashnag_staf.value_translated: Uno de los artefactos propios de Ushoran, este bastón supuestamente permitió al patriarca Strigoi original contener la agresión de los Lahmianos durante tanto tiempo.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gausser_axe.value_original: A Dwarf's grudge is forever, but so is his gratitude for many lives saved. The unexpected gift of a family runic axe is to be remembered for just as long.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gausser_axe.value_translated: El rencor de un Enano es eterno, pero también lo es su gratitud por tantas vidas salvadas. El inesperado regalo de un hacha rúnica familiar será recordado durante el mismo tiempo.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gausser_scar.value_original: Formerly a magic and fluttering arabyan turban, this souvenir bears energetic enchantments. The cadre of Myrmidian priests who prodded it for a week have testified that the scarf won't strangle Gausser of its own initiative anytime soon, which is oddly specific.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_gausser_scar.value_translated: Antiguamente un mágico y ondeante turbante arabyano, este recuerdo porta enérgicos encantamientos. El grupo de sacerdotes mirmidianos que la han picaneado durante una semana han atestiguado que la bufanda no estrangulará a Gausser por iniciativa propia en un futuro próximo, lo que resulta extrañamente específico.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lorenzo_lupo.value_original: A ring bearing the cameo of Luccina, sorceress and sister of Lucan. This enchanted item sings inspiring hymns and exhortations that embolden nearby troops.
This ancient shield might predate the city of Luccini, and still embodies the power of the sun.
This blade is believed to be the actual sword used by his remote ancestor, Lucan, one of the twin divine founders of Luccini.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lucrezzia_st.value_original: Lucrezzia always wears, somewhere on her person, a dagger coated with another of her brews. Can't blame someone for being prepared for a midnight stab.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lucrezzia_st.value_translated: Lucrezzia siempre lleva, en algún lugar de su persona, una daga recubierta con otro de sus brebajes. No se puede culpar a nadie por estar preparado para una puñalada a medianoche.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lupio_cloak.value_original: A cloak made of Lustrian gold, with uncertain magic properties. Its known feature is to give Lupio immense satisfaction.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lupio_cloak.value_translated: Capa de oro lusitano con propiedades mágicas inciertas. Su característica conocida es que proporciona a Lupio una inmensa satisfacción.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lupio_foot_a.value_original: Some people mistake Lupio's battlefield antics for astute shows of force and bravery for the troops. Truth is, they're Lupio's own satisfaction.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lupio_foot_a.value_translated: Algunas personas confunden las payasadas de Lupio en el campo de batalla con astutas demostraciones de fuerza y valentía para las tropas. La verdad es que son una satisfacción del propio Lupio.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lupio_ring.value_original: Reaped during a confusing skirmish against reptiles, elf corsairs and marauders, this ring bears an eerie and intriguing aura over it. Inquisitors never managed to get it off Lupio for investigation.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_lupio_ring.value_translated: Cosechado durante una confusa escaramuza contra reptiles, corsarios elfos y merodeadores, este anillo lleva sobre sí un aura inquietante e intrigante. Los inquisidores nunca consiguieron quitárselo a Lupio para investigarlo.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_merc_captain.value_original: Horse plate bardings are expensive, but might stop the heathen or monster from killing your mount outright.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_merc_captain.value_translated: Los bardos con placa de caballo son caros, pero pueden evitar que un pagano o un monstruo mate a tu montura.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_merc_general.value_original: Horse plate bardings are expensive, but might stop the heathen or monster from killing your mount outright.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_merc_general.value_translated: Los caballos con armadura son caros, pero pueden evitar que un pagano o un monstruo mate a tu montura.

ancillaries_colour_text_teb_merc_general.value_original: Nothing beats a Griffon mount to make everyone respect your authoritah.
ancillaries_colour_text_teb_merc_general.value_translated: No hay nada mejor que un Grifo para que todos respeten tu autoridad.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_conspi_h.value_original: "Sir, I dare say you should stop intruding in public conversations and pretending to be part of them. No, sir, the white hood doesn't make you look enigmatic or dashing at all. Merely runny."
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_conspi_h.value_translated: "Señor, me atrevería a decir que debería dejar de entrometerse en las conversaciones públicas y pretender formar parte de ellas. No, señor, la capucha blanca no le hace parecer enigmático ni gallardo en absoluto. Meramente cursi".

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_duellist.value_original: In Tilea, a cloak could hide a deadly dagger, or it could just show off ermine and velvet. Sometimes it's both.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_duellist.value_translated: En Tilea, una capa puede ocultar una daga mortal, o simplemente lucir armiño y terciopelo. A veces, ambas cosas.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_idol_myr.value_original: A delicate statuette of the Goddess, beautiful and useful to show off religious piety. Sometimes it also whispers of tactics in the owner's mind.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_idol_myr.value_translated: Una delicada estatuilla de la Diosa, hermosa y útil para mostrar piedad religiosa. A veces también susurra tácticas en la mente de su dueño.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_jewel_sw.value_original: This marvellous and shiny weapon is so skillfully done that a trained leader can lead an army to victory in a rainbow of sun glares. It is absolutely worthless in actual combat, though.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_jewel_sw.value_translated: Esta maravillosa y brillante arma está hecha con tanta destreza que un líder entrenado puede conducir a un ejército a la victoria en un arco iris de destellos de sol. Sin embargo, es absolutamente inútil en combate real.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_renegade.value_original: This simple circlet is the symbol of unification dreams for the Borderlands, and anybody wearing it would be the leader of the squabbling Princes, or their worst enemy, or just a puppet...
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_renegade.value_translated: Esta sencilla corona es el símbolo de los sueños de unificación de las Tierras Fronterizas, y cualquiera que la lleve podría ser el líder de los Príncipes en disputa, o su peor enemigo, o simplemente una marioneta...

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_retracta.value_original: The perfect weapon if you want complex, ineffective, concealed and showy at the same time and if you ask the right customer.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_retracta.value_translated: El arma perfecta si quieres algo complejo, ineficaz, oculto y vistoso a la vez, y si se lo pides al cliente adecuado.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_secrets.value_original: A pain-stakingly compiled registry of awkward and dangerous secrets of the owner's enemies. For good measure, it is said to be enchanted to fly away and replicate should something happen to the possessor...
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_secrets.value_translated: Un registro minuciosamente compilado de secretos incómodos y peligrosos de los enemigos del propietario. Por si fuera poco, se dice que está encantada para volar y reproducirse en caso de que le ocurra algo a su poseedor...

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_ser_gene.value_original: A jester who is the split image of the Duke of Bordeleaux, highly liked in courts for all sorts of parodies and shenanigans.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_ser_gene.value_translated: Un bufón que es la viva imagen del Duque de Bordeleaux, muy apreciado en las cortes por todo tipo de parodias y travesuras.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_shield_m.value_original: An ancient-looking shield found in the Acropolis of Luccini, capable of blinding foes. Presumably a copy.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_shield_m.value_translated: Escudo de aspecto antiguo hallado en la Acrópolis de Luccini, capaz de cegar a los enemigos. Presumiblemente una copia.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_spear_he.value_original: A spear said to have been in the possession of holy Sister Fury, hungry for a foe's demise.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_spear_he.value_translated: Una lanza que se dice estuvo en posesión de la santa Hermana Furia, hambrienta de la muerte de un enemigo.

ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_ugoletti.value_original: The engineer responsible for the rework of Da Miragliano's tank design and their maintenance. Technobabble guaranteed, sanity optional.
ancillaries_colour_text_tebuary_ugoletti.value_translated: El ingeniero responsable de la reelaboración del diseño de los tanques de Da Miragliano y de su mantenimiento. Tecnicismo garantizado, cordura opcional.

ancillaries_colour_text_til_merchant_bea.value_original: "Why so surprised? Anybody can get one of these! I just bought it off some Gryphon Legion fellow."

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ar.value_original: Those who don this enchanted plate armour gain Geheb's strength and favour, enabling them to parry a normally-lethal blow with a seemingly-lucky deflection.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ar.value_translated: Los que se ponen esta armadura de placas encantada obtienen la fuerza y el favor de Geheb, lo que les permite parar un golpe normalmente letal con un desvío aparentemente afortunado.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ar.value_original: This helm, inscribed with an invocation to the malign Desert-God, so that his savage ferocity may overtake its wearer.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ar.value_translated: Este yelmo lleva inscrita una invocación al maligno Dios del Desierto, para que su salvaje ferocidad se apodere de su portador.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ar.value_original: These ornate armour plates are decorated with the likeness of the Scorpion-God; his protective energies pervade the very metal used, offering additional protection to the wearer.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ar.value_translated: Estas placas de armadura ornamentadas están decoradas con la imagen del Dios Escorpión; sus energías protectoras impregnan el propio metal utilizado, ofreciendo protección adicional al portador.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_en.value_original: Having witnessed the doom of thousands over the course of the centuries, death's fell taint hangs heavy upon Prince Kharnut's expressionless mask, with terror forever close behind.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_en.value_translated: Tras haber sido testigo de la perdición de miles de personas a lo largo de los siglos, la mancha de la muerte pesa sobre la máscara inexpresiva del príncipe Kharnut, siempre seguida de cerca por el terror.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_en.value_original: This dark, ragged shroud is imbued with Sokth's treacherous essence, enabling them to stalk their enemies unseen until the final moment.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_en.value_translated: Este sudario oscuro y andrajoso está imbuido de la esencia traicionera de Sokth, lo que les permite acechar a sus enemigos sin ser vistos hasta el momento final.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_en.value_original: Infused with the sun's dazzling intensity, the power harnessed within gleams brilliantly, blinding the wearer's opponents.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_en.value_translated: Impregnado con la deslumbrante intensidad del sol, el poder que encierra brilla intensamente, cegando a los oponentes de su portador.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_original: This moon-shaped amulet projects a disruptive magical energy onto the enemy's defences.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_translated: Este amuleto en forma de luna proyecta una energía mágica disruptiva sobre las defensas del enemigo.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_original: This Nehekharan symbol of eternity surrounds its wearer with a protective aura of magical energy.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_translated: Este símbolo nehekhariano de eternidad rodea a su portador con un aura protectora de energía mágica.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_original: This sigil, carved into the war chariot of King Rah-Nutt, caused arrows and spears glance harmlessly away as he rode into battle.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_translated: Este sigilo, tallado en el carro de guerra del rey Rah-Nutt, hacía que flechas y lanzas se alejaran inofensivamente mientras cabalgaba hacia la batalla.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_original: This precious stone glows with the rising of the sun, gifting its bearer with the Great Father's divine protection.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_ta.value_translated: Esta piedra preciosa brilla con la salida del sol, otorgando a su portador la protección divina del Gran Padre.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_we.value_original: This Tomb Prince's magical sword draws lifeforce from the slain to imbue the body of its wielder with stolen essence.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_we.value_translated: Esta espada mágica del Príncipe Tumulario extrae la fuerza vital de los muertos para imbuir el cuerpo de su portador con la esencia robada.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_we.value_original: This enchanted, impossibly-sharp blade can cleave through armour, flesh, bone and souls with equal ease, reducing victims to a lifeless husk.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_dlc09_anc_we.value_translated: Esta hoja encantada e imposiblemente afilada puede atravesar armaduras, carne, huesos y almas con la misma facilidad, reduciendo a las víctimas a una cáscara sin vida.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: This chainmail is exceptionally shiny; that's impressive, considering it's Skaven-made!
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: Esta cota de malla es excepcionalmente brillante; ¡es impresionante, teniendo en cuenta que está hecha por Skaven!

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: Although battered and scarred, the shield is a treasured heirloom from the days Dragons freely roamed the skies.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: Aunque maltrecho y lleno de cicatrices, el escudo es una preciada reliquia de los días en que los dragones surcaban libremente los cielos.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: A helm of ithilmar and sea gold, bordered with intertwining runic script that form a prayer to invoke Asuryan's protection.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: Un yelmo de ithilmar y oro marino, bordeado de escrituras rúnicas entrelazadas que forman una plegaria para invocar la protección de Asuryan.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: While these Skryre-crafted boots cannot lift the wearer off the ground, they surely make him fleeter of foot!
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: Aunque estas botas fabricadas en Skryre no pueden levantar al portador del suelo, ¡seguro que lo hacen más ágil!

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: The tormented soul of an assassin is eternally bound to this cold shroud.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: El alma atormentada de un asesino está eternamente ligada a esta fría mortaja.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: A truly dreadful helmet, adorned as it is with the skulls of children.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: Un yelmo verdaderamente espantoso, adornado con cráneos de niños.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: The shield is a more a weapon than for protection, its bearer able to hack and slash with the barbed edges.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: El escudo es más un arma que una protección, y su portador es capaz de cortar y acuchillar con los filos.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_original: Such boots grant the wearer a boost of speed; companions tacitly ignore the little wings on the sides.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_arm.value_translated: Estas botas otorgan al portador un impulso de velocidad; los compañeros ignoran tácitamente las pequeñas alas de los laterales.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: What is in the box? No-one knows, but the sounds it produces makes even the bravest flee in mortal terror!
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: ¿Qué contiene la caja? Nadie lo sabe, pero los sonidos que produce hacen que hasta el más valiente huya despavorido.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: Grim resolve fills the heart of those that hear this clarion.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: Una sombría determinación llena el corazón de los que escuchan este clarín.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: This wooden and bone chest contains great bounty.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: Este cofre de madera y huesos contiene una gran recompensa.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: The Shield of the Old Ones grows more powerful under the influence of this glowing plaque.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: El Escudo de los Antiguos se hace más poderoso bajo la influencia de esta placa brillante.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: An ancient vestment enchanted by the eccentric Mage, Folariath.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: Una antigua vestidura encantada por el excéntrico mago Folariath.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: The most feared of all Elven magical rings is the black iron Ring of Fury, belonging to Khaine, the Bloody-handed God of Murder.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: El más temido de todos los anillos mágicos élficos es el Anillo de la Furia, de hierro negro, perteneciente a Khaine, el Dios Sangriento del Asesinato.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: A ring of a wrathful god will make its bearer faster, and more aggressive in his outlook.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: El anillo de un dios iracundo hará que su portador sea más rápido y más agresivo en su forma de actuar.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_original: The cloak is made from the feathers of the mysterious Coatl, shimmering with a power to ward against dark sorcery.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_enc.value_translated: La capa está hecha de plumas del misterioso Coatl, que brillan con un poder que protege contra la hechicería oscura.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_original: The bearer of this amethyst amulet knows things no mortal should.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_translated: El portador de este amuleto de amatista sabe cosas que ningún mortal debería saber.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_original: A dark crown, that will ensorcel the heart of those that bear it.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_translated: Una corona oscura que ensorcelará el corazón de quien la lleve.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_original: Made from gold of the Blackspine Mountains, the Deathmask depicts Khaine in his aspect of the Deathbringer.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_translated: Hecha de oro de las Montañas Espinazo Negro, la Máscara de la Muerte representa a Khaine en su aspecto de Portador de la Muerte.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_original: The Emerald Collar is a gold band encrusted with cursed stones.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_translated: El Collar de Esmeralda es una banda de oro con incrustaciones de piedras malditas.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_original: The size of the artefact known as the Talisman of Saphery belies its power, negating the effects of enchanted weapons against the bearer.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_translated: El tamaño del artefacto, conocido como Talismán de Saphery, contradice su poder, ya que anula los efectos de las armas encantadas contra su portador.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_original: The amulet is a lustrous polished stone with a midnight hue, engraved with a single spiteful rune.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_translated: El amuleto es una lustrosa piedra pulida con un tono medianoche, grabada con una única runa malévola.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_original: These golden bracers are fabled to have been found on the shores of distant Lustria and are inscribed with unusual glyphs.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_tal.value_translated: Según la leyenda, estos brazales dorados se encontraron en las costas de la lejana Lustria y llevan inscritos glifos inusuales.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_wea.value_original: To the valiant, this blade lends supernatural speed and vigour; to the craven and corrupt, it brings only swift death.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_wea.value_translated: A los valientes, esta espada les proporciona una velocidad y un vigor sobrenaturales; a los cobardes y corruptos, sólo les trae una muerte rápida.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_wea.value_original: A dire lance, etched with the fiery blood of Dragons. It is much feared by High Elf Princes from the realm of Caledor.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh2_main_anc_wea.value_translated: Una lanza funesta, grabada con la sangre ardiente de los dragones. Es muy temida por los príncipes elfos del reino de Caledor.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_dlc03_anc_arm.value_original: Trollhide confers some of the more gruesome abilities of its former occupant to the wearer!
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_dlc03_anc_arm.value_translated: La piel de troll confiere a su portador algunas de las habilidades más horripilantes de su antiguo ocupante.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_dlc07_anc_arm.value_original: This breastplate, inscribed with the Grail Vow, knits otherwise mortal wounds together so its wearer can fight another day.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_dlc07_anc_arm.value_translated: Esta coraza, inscrita con el Voto del Grial, une heridas que de otro modo serían mortales para que su portador pueda luchar un día más.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_dlc07_anc_enc.value_original: When woven within a living horse’s mane, hair from Gille’s steed confers strength and resilience into mounts of the same noble bloodline.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_dlc07_anc_enc.value_translated: Cuando se entreteje con la crin de un caballo vivo, el pelo del corcel de Gille confiere fuerza y resistencia a las monturas del mismo noble linaje.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_armo.value_original: Those who don the Armour of Fortune seem to have the favour of Ranald, able to parry the lethal blow with a lucky deflection.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_armo.value_translated: Los que llevan la Armadura de la Fortuna parecen contar con el favor de Ranald, capaz de parar el golpe letal con un desvío afortunado.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_armo.value_original: Forged from a rare star metal, it is said that no mortal blade can piece the Armour of Meteoric Iron.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_armo.value_translated: Forjada con un raro metal estelar, se dice que ninguna hoja mortal puede romper la Armadura de Hierro Meteórico.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_armo.value_original: A dingy, battered helmet that looks like any other – but this is the Trickster’s Helm, a powerful artefact that protects the wearer.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_armo.value_translated: Un yelmo sucio y maltrecho que se parece a cualquier otro, pero es el Yelmo del Embaucador, un poderoso artefacto que protege a su portador.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_moun.value_original: Battle Wizards are rarely armoured for it interferes with their casting, yet a steed can and should be barded to add a level of protection.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_moun.value_translated: Los magos de batalla no suelen llevar armadura, ya que interfiere con sus invocaciones. Sin embargo, un corcel puede y debe llevar barbas para añadir un nivel de protección.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_moun.value_original: Imperial pegasi are found in Grey Mountains where Bretonnian and Empire hunters fight over capturing the foals.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_moun.value_translated: Los pegasi imperiales se encuentran en las Montañas Grises, donde los cazadores bretonianos e imperiales se pelean por capturar a los potros.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_original: An enchanted duo of blades - one long and one short - give the wielder a dazzling array of skilful moves, to parry and deceive an opponent.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_translated: Un dúo de espadas encantadas, una larga y otra corta, proporcionan a su portador una deslumbrante variedad de hábiles movimientos para esquivar y engañar al oponente.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_original: The Ogre Blade was used by Chaos Dwarfs to tame the kingdoms amongst the Mountains of Mourn. How it came to the Old World is a mystery.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_translated: Los Enanos del Caos utilizaron la Hoja del Ogro para domar los reinos de las Montañas del Luto. Cómo llegó al Viejo Mundo es un misterio.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_original: This blade was stolen from a Tomb Banshee while she sang a haunting nursery tale to a forgotten child. Now the blade sings too, and shrieks when it strikes a foe.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_translated: Esta hoja fue robada a una Banshee de la Tumba mientras cantaba un inquietante cuento infantil a un niño olvidado. Ahora la espada también canta, y chilla cuando golpea a un enemigo.

ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_original: A sword tinged red, for wherever it is swung bloodshed is guaranteed, with multiple foes falling in a single deadly arc.
ancillaries_colour_text_wh_main_anc_weap.value_translated: Una espada teñida de rojo, porque dondequiera que se blande, el derramamiento de sangre está garantizado, con múltiples enemigos cayendo en un único arco mortal.

ancillaries_onscreen_name_mount_bor_rang.value_translated: Caballo de guerra y arma de repetición

ancillaries_onscreen_name_mount_teb_colo.value_translated: Corcel élfico con bardas y ballesta de la muerte

ancillaries_onscreen_name_teb_duellist_h.value_translated: Caballo de guerra con barda y puntal de pistolas

ancillaries_onscreen_name_teb_duellist_h.value_original: Barded Warhorse & Lots of Red Paint
ancillaries_onscreen_name_teb_duellist_h.value_translated: Caballo de guerra con barda y mucha pintura roja

ancillaries_onscreen_name_wh2_dlc09_anc_.value_translated: Máscara de la muerte de Kharnut

ancillary_sets_description_teb_anci_set_.value_original: Quite stabby and fashionable, but also delusional.
"Am I out of touch? No, it's the peasants who are miserly!"

building_culture_variants_name_teb_homel.value_translated: Cabeza de Playa de los Conquistadores

building_effect_context_expressions_disp.value_original: When any [[img:icon_general]][[/img]]Mercenary Camp is in the region:

building_sets_onscreen_description_teb_d.value_original: Towers and garrisons to defend the city against invaders.

building_sets_onscreen_description_teb_e.value_original: Even in times of war, industry and infrastructure will always be required.

building_sets_onscreen_description_teb_m.value_original: Improve the quality of your units and recruit mighty [[img:icon_hero]][[/img]]Heroes to bolster your armies.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Outposts from the Southern Realms are generally little more than bodyguards around a mercantile enterprise.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los puestos avanzados de los Reinos del Sur suelen ser poco más que guardaespaldas en torno a una empresa mercantil.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Tilea and Estalia have districts within the settlements of lands as far afield as Lustria, Ulthuan and even the Far East.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Tilea y Estalia tienen distritos dentro de los asentamientos de tierras tan lejanas como Lustria, Ulthuan e incluso el Lejano Oriente.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Strong embassies around the world guarantee the flow of commerce and mercenaries.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Fuertes embajadas en todo el mundo garantizan el flujo de comercio y mercenarios.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Raw genius, shapeless marble and lumps of dye can become breathtaking works of art. The South has plenty of all of them.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: El genio en bruto, el mármol sin forma y los grumos de tinte pueden convertirse en impresionantes obras de arte. En el Sur abundan todos ellos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Paid local militias can be given basic training, and all the clamour can attract better soldiers.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Las milicias locales pagadas pueden recibir formación básica, y todo el clamor puede atraer a mejores soldados.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Citizens are rarely enthusiastic soldiers, but with enough effort they can be put into shape together with the local mercenary bands.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los ciudadanos rara vez son soldados entusiastas, pero con el suficiente esfuerzo se les puede poner en forma junto con las bandas de mercenarios locales.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Given enough time and money, local militias and some of the reliable companies can be trained to work together.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Con tiempo y dinero suficientes, se puede entrenar a las milicias locales y a algunas de las compañías fiables para que trabajen juntas.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A small mobile workshop that keeps field artillery working and not exploding.
The best the camp can get, from forges to experienced crewmen with their distinctive tinnitus and lack of eyebrows.
PLACEHOLDER
PLACEHOLDER
PLACEHOLDER
The camp has its own cavalry, and its distinctive smell.
Fancier riders, fancier horses, and still the unintelligible lingo of horse handlers.
Professional riders orbit the camp, and help secure victories.
PLACEHOLDER
PLACEHOLDER
Some foreign mercenaries spontaneously come to the Southern Realms with some regularity. They may have odd customs, but who doesn't.
An army marches or encamps on its stomach.
Especially the Halflings.
And the Ogres.
Supplies, mothertucker!
Enough supplies for a literal army, or two or three.
PLACEHOLDER
PLACEHOLDER
PLACEHOLDER
PLACEHOLDER
PLACEHOLDER
"Men with sticks! Sticks with men! Stick-men! All are welcome here!"
"On second thought, let's get some half-decent fighters too."
"And that rat-man horde isn't going to kill itself..."
"...not quickly enough, anyway."
PLACEHOLDER
"Look, guys, the guides here are not lascivious blondes in skimpy outfits. No, shut up. We're lucky to have found Bob the lizard here."
Build the best camp in the world, or I'll eat your souls!
And we wrote the first thing that came to our heads-
-It just so happened to be.
The best camp in the world.
It was the best camp in the world.
Shooting people and monsters with crossbows! Finest tradition in the south.
This shooting range will do for the most part. Drunk mercs occasionally waddle in, but it adds to the challenge.
"And for my next demonstration, I shall hit the target after pirhouetting full-circle, without aiming and while jumping on the spot!"
PLACEHOLDER

"Aren't you a little short to be a mercen-"
The many ports of the South are not only vehicles for commerce, but contribute to the various mercenary companies finding new shores and habitats. Nature is beautiful.
"Whether you're here for the booze or to impress the ladies, we got room for you."
"Next! Next! Next!"
"No, I said no Goblins! Alright, fine, but it's your responsibility!"
"No, that is not a dragon and you are not Asarnil. How do I- it just oinked at me!"
"Look, if you can ride the pig well enough you can get in a lance company at half pay. Next!"
"You got what stuck where?"
"Yes, yes, lay down next to Inigo."
"WILL YOU IDIOTS STOP DYING?"
"This is fine."
"I should have stayed at the farm."
"This foreboding sign would probably stop me if I could read."
Know a man's worth, and what he ain't.
The click-clack of a big abacus, and the stare of much bigger Maneater guards.
The future of the entire camp under a safe lock.
Money goes in, money goes out, money all around.
And around and around it goes.
Just dropping the goods on the piers won't do. Having efficient storage in a strategic position is key to good commerce.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: No basta con dejar las mercancías en los muelles. Disponer de un almacén eficiente en una posición estratégica es clave para un buen comercio.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Just dropping the goods on the piers won't do. Having efficient storage in a strategic position is key to good commerce.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: No basta con depositar las mercancías en los muelles. Contar con un almacenamiento eficiente en una posición estratégica es clave para un buen comercio.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Well-organized depots, marketplaces and networks are the lifeblood of a mercantile system. And with enough goods in its veins, merchants will engage in advanced finance over products that are yet to be shipped or even produced.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Unos depósitos, mercados y redes bien organizados son la savia de un sistema mercantil. Y con suficientes mercancías en sus venas, los mercaderes se involucrarán en finanzas avanzadas sobre productos que aún no han sido enviados o incluso producidos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Well-organized depots, marketplaces and networks are the lifeblood of a mercantile system. And with enough goods in its veins, merchants will engage in advanced finance over products that are yet to be shipped or even produced.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Depósitos, mercados y redes bien organizados son la savia de un sistema mercantil. Y con suficientes mercancías en sus venas, los comerciantes se dedicarán a la financiación avanzada de productos que aún no han sido enviados o incluso producidos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Well-organized depots, marketplaces and networks are the lifeblood of a mercantile system. And with enough goods in its veins, merchants will engage in advanced finance over products that are yet to be shipped or even produced.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Depósitos, mercados y redes bien organizados son la savia de un sistema mercantil. Y con suficientes mercancías en sus venas, los mercaderes se dedicarán a la financiación avanzada de productos que aún no han sido enviados o incluso producidos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: With the promise of loot, professional soldiery is imported from the mainlands.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Con la promesa del botín, se importan soldados profesionales de las tierras continentales.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Inspired by the success of the colonies, major forces are made available from the homeland.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Inspirados por el éxito de las colonias, se ponen a disposición importantes fuerzas de la patria.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: As the colony flourishes, entire powerful retinues are assembled, both local and imported.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: A medida que la colonia florece, se reúnen poderosos séquitos enteros, tanto locales como importados.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Built upon the Sapphire Gate, this fortress makes sure there are more arbalests on the walls than resentful Elves inside.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Construida sobre la Puerta de Zafiro, esta fortaleza se asegura de que haya más Ballesteros en las murallas que elfos resentidos en su interior.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A respectful trading quarter, an expansion and improvement upon the existing Foreigners Quarter. Mutual benefits, at discreet rates.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Un respetuoso barrio comercial, una ampliación y mejora del Barrio de los Extranjeros ya existente. Beneficios mutuos, a precios discretos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The ancient city of Luccini is built on elven ruins, but its temples are all too human. The Temple of Luccina is sacred to the city's peculiar rulers, and the Temple of Morr is one of the main chapterhouses for the god's knightly order.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: La antigua ciudad de Luccina está construida sobre ruinas élficas, pero sus templos son demasiado humanos. El Templo de Luccina es sagrado para los peculiares gobernantes de la ciudad, y el Templo de Morr es una de las principales salas capitulares de la orden de caballeros del dios.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A simple encampment with a well-visible "HYRING" sign is often enough to draw a conspicuous force of mercenaries that won't mind the spelling.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Un simple campamento con un cartel bien visible de "Riclutamento" suele bastar para atraer a una fuerza llamativa de mercenarios a los que no les importará la ortografía.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A larger recruitment building, compulsorily next to a tavern and reasonably close to a brothel, will draw more than the usual cutthroat.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Un edificio de reclutamiento más grande, obligatoriamente al lado de una taberna y razonablemente cerca de un burdel, atraerá a más de los habituales degolladores.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Famed condottieri, adventuring knights, scarred veterans, exotic warriors, all in one well-organized and relatively peaceful hub.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Famosos condottieri, caballeros aventureros, veteranos con cicatrices, guerreros exóticos, todo en un centro bien organizado y relativamente tranquilo.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Paying mercenaries to do your fighting is handy. However, you often end up paying more for them to stop fighting you.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Pagar a mercenarios para que luchen es muy útil. Sin embargo, a menudo acabas pagando más para que dejen de luchar contra ti.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Regiments and warbands that are normally kept in check are abundant and unruly, attracted by easy money and entertainment. The populace is definitely unhappy.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los regimientos y bandas de guerra que normalmente se mantienen a raya son abundantes y revoltosos, atraídos por el dinero fácil y el entretenimiento. La población está definitivamente descontenta.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The province has seen better days, as entire armies of mercenaries obey their own whims and unscrupulous commanders more than any local Prince.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: La provincia ha visto días mejores, ya que ejércitos enteros de mercenarios obedecen más a sus propios caprichos y a comandantes sin escrúpulos que a cualquier príncipe local.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Cannon foundries are uncommon in the South, but Tilean engineers are deemed "acceptable" even by Dwarfs.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Las fundiciones de cañones son poco comunes en el Sur, pero los ingenieros tileanos son considerados "aceptables" incluso por los enanos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Cannon foundries are uncommon in the South, but Tilean engineers are deemed "acceptable" even by Dwarfs.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Las fundiciones de cañones son poco comunes en el Sur, pero los ingenieros tileanos son considerados "aceptables" incluso por los enanos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: City barracks can put militias in shape, together with locally available mercenaries.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los cuarteles de la ciudad pueden poner en forma a las milicias, junto con los mercenarios disponibles localmente.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Given enough time and money, local militias and some of the reliable companies can be trained to work together.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Con tiempo y dinero suficientes, las milicias locales y algunas de las compañías fiables pueden entrenarse para trabajar juntas.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The best that a large city can offer locally, if the local Prince doesn't want to bother with too many mercenaries in the same place.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Lo mejor que una gran ciudad puede ofrecer localmente, si el Príncipe local no quiere molestarse con demasiados mercenarios en el mismo lugar.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: teb_mil_duellists_1
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: teb_mil_duellists_1

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: teb_mil_duellists_2
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: teb_mil_duellists_2

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A simple encampment with a well-visible "HYRING" sign is often enough to draw a conspicuous force of mercenaries that won't mind the spelling.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Un simple campamento con un cartel bien visible de "Riclutamento" suele bastar para atraer a una fuerza llamativa de mercenarios a los que no les importará la ortografía.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Southern mercenaries tend to be vastly more professional than their colleagues, and this city's infrastructure will attract legions of them.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los mercenarios sureños suelen ser mucho más profesionales que sus colegas, y la infraestructura de esta ciudad atraerá a legiones de ellos.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Scarred veterans and exotic warriors, all in one well-organized and relatively peaceful hub.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Veteranos con cicatrices y guerreros exóticos, todo en un centro bien organizado y relativamente pacífico.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Greenskin-afflicted villagers who dream of being saved by a swift ranger probably didn't imagine his breath and smell accurately enough.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los aldeanos afectados por pieles verdes que sueñan con ser salvados por un veloz guardabosques probablemente no imaginaron su aliento y olor con suficiente precisión.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The borderlands are dangerous places for dangerous men. Some of them are on the local prince's payroll.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Las tierras fronterizas son lugares peligrosos para hombres peligrosos. Algunos de ellos están en nómina del príncipe local.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Restored and enlarged, Miragliano's channel system is a unique panorama of bridges and leaning towers, accurately safeguarded from infiltrating ratmen.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Restaurado y ampliado, el sistema de canales de Miragliano es un panorama único de puentes y torres inclinadas, salvaguardado con precisión de los rateros infiltrados.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Within these walls and halls, the garrison was inspired by the spirited Monna Lissa to defend the fabulous frescoes therein almost to the last man. True Tileans will die fighting rather than let anything happen to Tintoverdi's Five Seasons.
The many secrets of Ushoran still lie in these ruins, for those who can learn.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los muchos secretos de Ushoran aún yacen en estas ruinas, para aquellos que puedan aprender.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Mistakes were made. Mistakes will be repeated, because such is Fate.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Se cometieron errores. Los errores se repetirán, porque así es el destino.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: "That big, ugly, mutated thing is a walking treasure hoard. Go on, shoot it down."
Norscan stone is filled with precious stuff that nobody claimed before, although some of the rocks fight back.
Vast empires are crude. Why bother micro-managing when you can direct subjects and allies from your seat of power?
Good iron ore is a precious commodity, propelling steel quality in the region.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: El buen mineral de hierro es un bien preciado que impulsa la calidad del acero en la región.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Only premium steel here, for premium prices!
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Aquí sólo hay acero de primera, a precios de primera.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Plenty of quality timber isn't just prettier firewood, and can be used for sturdier weapons and buildings.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: La madera abundante y de calidad no sólo es una leña más bonita, sino que puede utilizarse para armas y edificios más resistentes.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: There is an art in making full use of good trees.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Hay un arte en aprovechar al máximo los buenos árboles.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Unknown tablets and mysterious stones are found in this region, for now unceremoniously sent to the homeland as proof of success.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: En esta región se encuentran tablillas desconocidas y piedras misteriosas, que por ahora se envían sin ceremonias a la patria como prueba del éxito.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Sizable amounts of artefacts are being found and smelt or otherwise traded home, for they are fetching a nice price.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Se encuentran cantidades considerables de artefactos que se funden o se comercian con ellos, pues alcanzan un buen precio.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Unknown tables and mysterious stones are found in this region... There is more in this than it catches the eye.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Tablas desconocidas y piedras misteriosas se encuentran en esta región... Hay más de lo que parece.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Invaluable artefacts are being recovered in the region, and traded to the neighbouring races for exorbitant rates.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: En la región se están recuperando artefactos de valor incalculable, que se comercian con las razas vecinas a precios exorbitantes.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Any small town may have a local farrier, but good weapon and armoursmiths tend to get reasonably wealthy where mercenaries come to buy and repair their gear.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Cualquier pueblo pequeño puede tener un herrero local, pero los buenos herreros de armas y armaduras tienden a hacerse razonablemente ricos allí donde los mercenarios acuden a comprar y reparar su equipo.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: With tricks of their own or dwarfen masters, southern smiths can produce quality gear and hallmark brass plate armour. Strong competition and high demand may drive to the creation of whole smithy districts and marketplaces.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Con trucos propios o de maestros enanos, los herreros sureños pueden producir equipo de calidad y armaduras de placas de latón con sello distintivo. La fuerte competencia y la gran demanda pueden llevar a la creación de distritos de herrería y mercados enteros.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Horses need tending, even for the lowliest local scout.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los caballos necesitan cuidados, incluso para el más humilde explorador local.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: There is a good market for good steeds when good mounted companies are invited to work in the area. With good money.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Hay un buen mercado para los buenos corceles cuando se invita a buenas empresas montadoras a trabajar en la zona. Con buen dinero.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Local nobles may own their own horses, but encouraging healthy manageries to tend and renew the stock is necessary.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los nobles locales pueden poseer sus propios caballos, pero es necesario animar a los administradores sanos a que cuiden y renueven el ganado.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Though incredibly expensive, this new type of bastion has no blind spots, is aesthetically pleasant, and is impervious to assaults and artillery. It may not be Shaggoth-proof.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Aunque increíblemente caro, este nuevo tipo de bastión no tiene puntos ciegos, es estéticamente agradable y es impermeable a los asaltos y a la artillería. Puede que no sea a prueba de Shaggoth.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The jungle can hide a lot of precious resources and fertile land. Plus, it's about time someone did something about the dog-sized mosquitoes.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: La jungla puede esconder muchos recursos valiosos y tierras fértiles. Además, ya es hora de que alguien haga algo con los mosquitos del tamaño de un perro.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: High mountains are unforgiving and possibly host to several annoyed monsters. Human adaptability can take care of both.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Las altas montañas son implacables y posiblemente alberguen a varios monstruos molestos. La adaptabilidad humana puede encargarse de ambas cosas.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Tobaro sits on rocks, most of them dangerous and many of them inhabited. The city has a history of Skaven infestations and invasions, which the scarred Deepwatch is trained to oppose.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Tobaro se asienta sobre rocas, la mayoría de ellas peligrosas y muchas de ellas habitadas. La ciudad tiene una historia de infestaciones e invasiones Skaven, a las que la cicatrizada Guardia Profunda está entrenada para oponerse.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The superhuman venture of cleansing the Skaven capital has begun. The surface is being purified by settlers, wizards and priests, but there is still fighting in the tunnels.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: La expedision sobrehumana de limpiar la capital Skaven ha comenzado. La superficie está siendo purificada por colonos, hechiceros y sacerdotes, pero aún se combate en los túneles.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The disinfestation is proceeding, humans can call the settlement a livable town again, relatively free from Skaven presence.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: La desinfestación avanza, los humanos pueden volver a considerar el asentamiento como una ciudad habitable, relativamente libre de la presencia Skaven.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The Doom of Kavzar is avenged! Tylos is reborn, a beacon of determination and wealth for all to see!
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: La perdición de Kavzar ha sido vengada. Tylos ha renacido, ¡un faro de determinación y riqueza a la vista de todos!

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: This is essentially still Skavenblight, but with a beachhead on top. Skaven still lurk just outside of a cautious perimeter.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: En esencia, esto sigue siendo Plagaskaven, pero con una cabeza de playa encima. Los Skaven aún acechan fuera de un perímetro cauteloso.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: The Skaven are being pushed away and downwards, but danger is still very present. Some brave souls are starting to call the place home.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Los Skaven están siendo empujados lejos y hacia abajo, pero el peligro sigue estando muy presente. Algunas almas valientes están empezando a llamar hogar al lugar.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Ambitious pioneers are jump-starting the rebirth of a new and old city, and cleaning up the place from the everpresent rabbles and dead rats.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Ambiciosos pioneros están poniendo en marcha el renacimiento de una nueva y vieja ciudad, y limpiando el lugar de los siempre presentes cangrejos y ratas muertas.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: Against even the most optimistic predictions, business is booming! The swamp is being sanitised and you can almost not smell rat anymore!
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: En contra de las predicciones más optimistas, el negocio está en auge. El pantano se está saneando y ya casi no huele a rata.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: For all the blood and sweat invested in it, the city is as powerful as any other human city-state, and a testament of determination. Now if only people could stop building towers.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: A pesar de toda la sangre y el sudor invertidos en ella, la ciudad es tan poderosa como cualquier otra ciudad-estado humana, y un testamento de determinación. Ojalá la gente dejara de construir torres.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A small effigy of Myrmidia, that recruits and mercenaries pray and salute to.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Una pequeña efigie de Myrmidia, a la que los reclutas y mercenarios rezan y saludan.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A small effigy of Shallya, usually attended with flowers and kind people.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Una pequeña efigie de Shallya, a la que suelen acudir flores y gente amable.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A small effigy of Shallya, usually attended with flowers and kind people.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Una pequeña efigie de Shallya, a la que suelen acudir flores y gente amable.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A temple to Shallya, that doubles as local infirmary and apothecary.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Un templo a Shallya, que hace las veces de enfermería y botica local.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A large temple to Shallya, that doubles as local infirmary and apothecary.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Un gran templo a Shallya, que también sirve de enfermería y botica.

building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_original: A large temple to Shallya, that doubles as local infirmary and apothecary.
building_short_description_texts_short_d.value_translated: Un gran templo a Shallya, que hace las veces de enfermería y botica local.
