This requires him to destroy all windmills in the world, particularly those that move by themselves. Despite people telling Lupio those are Giants, they clearly don't know better.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Lupio ha urdido en secreto el plan perfecto para mejorar drásticamente el bienestar de la región. Para ello debe destruir todos los molinos de viento del mundo, en particular los que se mueven solos. A pesar de que la gente le dice a Lupio que esos son Gigantes, está claro que no lo saben.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: There are few things that cannot be solved by excessive use of fire.
In a flash of polished armour and shiny robes, the Templar strikes fast and deadly.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: En un destello de armadura pulida y túnicas brillantes, el templario ataca rápido y mortal.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: The troops are led to amazing feats of bravery by the mere confidence of being guided by Myrmidia and one of Her skillful warriors.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Las tropas son conducidas a asombrosas hazañas de valentía por la mera confianza de ser guiadas por Myrmidia y uno de Sus hábiles guerreros.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Warrior Priests of Myrmidia are master tacticians known in the whole Old World.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Los Sacerdotes Guerreros de Myrmidia son maestros tácticos conocidos en todo el Viejo Mundo.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: "Oh, no, not another marathon at dawn."
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: "Oh, no, no otra maratón al amanecer".

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: The Templar's armour, naturally shiny, turns into an unsustainable beacon of light for the Forces of Destruction.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: La armadura del Templario, brillante por naturaleza, se convierte en un faro de luz insostenible para las Fuerzas de la Destrucción.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Charged with the Goddess' holy flame, the Templar's spear strikes the hardest when the arm is strong and the heart is pure. That's what she says, anyway.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Cargada con la llama sagrada de la diosa, la lanza del templario golpea con más fuerza cuando el brazo es fuerte y el corazón puro. Eso es lo que ella dice.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: A stance of mind and shield, and the enemy's onslaught is halted.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Una postura de mente y escudo, y la embestida del enemigo se detiene.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: A sure thrust in the foulest beast's heart can stop its meaningless flailing.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Una estocada certera en el corazón de la bestia más vil puede detener su agitar sin sentido.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: A Priestess or Templar of Myrmidia has every right to ride good estalian, arabyan or even bretonnian steeds into battle.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Una sacerdotisa o templaria de Myrmidia tiene todo el derecho a montar buenos corceles estalianos, arabianos o incluso bretonianos en la batalla.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: An excellent steed barded in stylish burnished steel, for the man that must not ask "Eh?".
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Un excelente corcel bardado en elegante acero bruñido, para el hombre que no debe preguntar "¿Eh?".

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: An exotic beast, the demigryph, mighty dangerous too. Whoever intends to tame and befriend one must be strong of will and limb, because even the best suits of plate are not demigryph-proof.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: El semigrifo es una bestia exótica y muy peligrosa. Quien pretenda domarla y entablar amistad con ella debe ser fuerte de voluntad y de miembros, porque ni siquiera las mejores armaduras son a prueba de semigrifos.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: A brilliant mind in a brilliant body, and both seem impossible to destroy.
In his training or previous command, this Templar has distinguished himself against the heathens. Bretonnian allies still have fond memories of him.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: En su formación o mando anterior, este Templario se ha distinguido contra los paganos. Los aliados bretonianos aún guardan buenos recuerdos de él.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: The wrath of Bellona Myrmidia rides this Templar's arm and strikes the impure with blazing might!
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: La ira de Bellona Myrmidia cabalga sobre el brazo de este templario y golpea a los impuros con un poder abrasador.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: This particular Knight was favoured with unanimity by the oracles of the Order of True Insight. That must have been expensive.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Este Caballero en particular fue favorecido con unanimidad por los oráculos de la Orden de la Verdadera Perspicacia. Debió de ser caro.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: "Respect the prisoners of war", says one of the major Myrmidian strictures. So this man does, honour and dignity above all. And tactical benefits.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: "Respeta a los prisioneros de guerra", dice una de las principales normas mirmidianas. Así lo hace este hombre, honor y dignidad por encima de todo. Y beneficios tácticos.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Fly on your wings, fly, and touch the sun.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Vuela con tus alas, vuela y toca el sol.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: The Templar’s righteousness is completely out of question, which is understandably uncommon.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: La rectitud del templario está completamente fuera de duda, lo que es comprensiblemente poco común.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: As the Templar’s troops come out of seemingly nowhere, the enemies scream his infamous name in frustration.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Mientras las tropas del Templario salen aparentemente de la nada, los enemigos gritan su infame nombre con frustración.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Behind the erudite mask of this Myrmidian commander lies the untamed spirit of a warrior. In battle, his arms glare of such a violent and supernatural light that even the untainted cannot stare for long.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Tras la máscara erudita de este comandante mirmidiano se esconde el espíritu indomable de un guerrero. En la batalla, sus brazos resplandecen de una luz tan violenta y sobrenatural que ni siquiera los impolutos pueden mirar fijamente durante mucho tiempo.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: The Templar’s mind is an incessant flow of tactical diagrams and pressure point markers.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: La mente del Templario es un flujo incesante de diagramas tácticos y marcadores de puntos de presión.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Mercenary hosts usually include powerful regiments with double pay and double the risks, once dubbed in Tilea "Duplicarii". The original meaning has gone lost, and the usual sense is now "You bunch of dog-botherers will better get it done, with what you cost me."
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Las huestes mercenarias suelen incluir poderosos regimientos con el doble de paga y el doble de riesgos, apodados antaño en Tilea "Doblepaga". El significado original se ha perdido, y el sentido habitual es ahora "Más os vale, panda de perroflautas, con lo que me habéis costado".

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: This commander has accrued a retinue of the sliest and shrewdest captains and guides available. Their advice is worth every silver coin.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Este comandante ha acumulado un séquito de los capitanes y guías más astutos y astutas disponibles. Sus consejos valen cada moneda de plata.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Knowledge that the enemy wallet might buy your troops out even before the first battle puts huge pressure to make sure it doesn't happen.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Saber que la cartera enemiga podría comprar a tus tropas incluso antes de la primera batalla ejerce una enorme presión para asegurarse de que eso no ocurra.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: War is merely the extension of economy by other means. But you do need someone to do the actual killing.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: La guerra no es más que la prolongación de la economía por otros medios. Pero se necesita a alguien que mate de verdad.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: This man can easily distinguish between an ancient elven magical sword of implacable might and a piece of shiny iron, which is not so simple when the artifact itself is in that disguise.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Este hombre puede distinguir fácilmente entre una antigua espada mágica élfica de poder implacable y un trozo de hierro brillante, lo que no es tan sencillo cuando el propio artefacto lleva ese disfraz.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Kill not, waste not.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: No matar, no desperdiciar.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Sometimes it is just time to party. The louder, the better.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: A veces sólo es hora de divertirse. Cuanto más ruidosa, mejor.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: A commander that allows his captains and troops to everything they can put their hands on is either irresponsible, well-adviced, criminally aggressive or all of the above.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Un comandante que permite a sus capitanes y tropas todo lo que se les ponga por delante es irresponsable, bien aconsejado, criminalmente agresivo o todo lo anterior.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: "Open the coffers, put up more signs. I want more cannons, pikes, even ogres, even those buggers with the paper wings. Everyone. I shall have that castle by tomorrow or by Myrmidia I will drown them in mercs."
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: "Abran las arcas, pongan más carteles. Quiero más cañones, picas, incluso ogros, incluso esos bichos con alas de papel. A todos. Tendré ese castillo para mañana o para Myrmidia los ahogaré en mercenarios".

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Money must flow.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: El dinero debe fluir.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Such is the pinnacle of the tilean merchant prince and politician that seemingly anything can be handled.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Tal es el pináculo del príncipe mercader y político tileano que aparentemente se puede manejar cualquier cosa.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: "People say that the colour of magic is purple, white, red... I say it is gold. For all that lot."
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: "La gente dice que el color de la magia es púrpura, blanco, rojo... Yo digo que es dorado. Por todo eso".

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Improving infrastructure and rebuilding the war-ravaged regions is key to a prosperous economy.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Mejorar las infraestructuras y reconstruir las regiones devastadas por la guerra es clave para una economía próspera.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Being supportive of the flourishing tilean art is prestigious, and prestige is lucrative.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Apoyar el floreciente arte tejano es prestigioso, y el prestigio es lucrativo.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Being known for actually paying one's hirelings - those that come back alive, anyway - pays off.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Ser conocido por pagar realmente a sus asalariados -los que vuelven vivos, al menos- vale la pena.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: "You know you're doing it right when everyone and their mamas are sending people to stab you."
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: "Sabes que lo estás haciendo bien cuando todo el mundo y sus madres envían gente a apuñalarte".

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Commerce is the life-blood of any economy, and the sea must be its heart.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: El comercio es la sangre vital de cualquier economía, y el mar debe ser su corazón.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Personally seizing the means of production never felt better.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Apoderarse personalmente de los medios de producción nunca se sintió mejor.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: This man has not gotten where he is now by being weak-minded.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: Este hombre no ha llegado donde está por ser débil de mente.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: The doubt that betrayal would hardly bring woes but even monetary incentives has turned the tables of many battles.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: La duda de que la traición no traería desgracias sino incluso incentivos monetarios ha cambiado las tornas de muchas batallas.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Costly gear lent to the mercenary companies may be expensive, but it may save the day and the treasury afterwards.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: El costoso equipo prestado a las compañías mercenarias puede ser caro, pero puede salvar el día y el tesoro después.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: Steel barding adds that certain something to your mount. A pity they didn't have it in red.
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: La armadura de acero le da ese toque especial a tu montura. Una pena que no lo tuvieran en rojo.

character_skills_localised_description_t.value_original: A horse! A horse! An acceptable amount of florins for a horse!
character_skills_localised_description_t.value_translated: ¡Un caballo! ¡Un caballo! ¡Una cantidad aceptable de florines por un caballo!

character_skills_localised_description_w.value_original: A pegasus is a noble, winged steed, intelligent and loyal, that few Hedge Wizards can afford or be rewarded with.
character_skills_localised_description_w.value_translated: Un pegaso es un noble corcel alado, inteligente y leal, que pocos Hedge Wizards pueden permitirse o con el que pueden ser recompensados.

character_skills_localised_description_w.value_original: Nothing beats a trusted Griffon mount to make everyone respect your authoritah.
character_skills_localised_description_w.value_translated: Nada mejor que una montura Grifo de confianza para que todos respeten su autoridad.

character_skills_localised_name_bor_rang.value_translated: Caballo de guerra y arma de mano de repetición

character_skills_localised_name_teb_army.value_translated: El combate cuerpo a cuerpo, Cap. I

character_skills_localised_name_teb_cada.value_translated: Cuento de Cadavo II: El Duelo
Cuento de Cadavo III: Habitación para uno
Historia de Cadavo IV: Entre la leyenda y el mito
Cuento de Cadavo V: Y así juró
Cuento de Cadavo V: Y así juró
Cuento de Cadavo V: Y así siguió adelante

character_skills_localised_name_teb_catr.value_original: The Very Best Money Can Buy
character_skills_localised_name_teb_catr.value_translated: Lo mejor que el dinero puede comprar

character_skills_localised_name_teb_colo.value_translated: Corcel Elfico con bardas y ballesta de la perdición
Caballo de guerra con barda y ballesta de la perdición

character_skills_localised_name_til_merc.value_translated: Lo mejor que el dinero puede comprar

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: "Alejandro, do this, Alejandro, do that. Alejandro, man the cannon. The worst is, I'm even going to do it."
The Besieger is defeated, they say falling on a toasting fork in shame. Hopefully, this time it sticks.
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: El Sitiador está derrotado, dicen cayendo sobre un tenedor de tostar avergonzado. Esperemos que esta vez se le pegue.

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: Finally, the mercenary commander has stopped being a nuisance and is headed towards greener pastures, or whatever he believ-what do you mean he’s back?
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: Por fin, el comandante mercenario ha dejado de ser un incordio y se dirige hacia pastos más verdes, o lo que él crea... ¿cómo que ha vuelto?

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: How many times do we have to teach you this lesson, you suspiciously middle-aged man?
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: ¿Cuántas veces tenemos que enseñarte esta lección, hombre sospechosamente maduro?
Esta vez se ha ido. Definitivamente

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: We know exactly where their money is, lads.
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: Sabemos exactamente dónde está su dinero, muchachos.

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: For all his contacts in Lustria, maybe he should have gone to Ind.
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: Con todos sus contactos en Lustria, quizá debería haber ido a la India.

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: Fighting him felt like being sixteen all over again.
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: Luchar contra él ha sido como volver a tener 16 años.

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: So, how many vampires are there, exactly?
Maybe you should have gathered your Dwarf friends to go steal a dragon's treasure, eh?
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: Quizá deberías haber reunido a tus amigos enanos para ir a robar el tesoro de un dragón, ¿eh?

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: "Curse? What curse, you meowling idiot, hah! Heh. Forget the dead meathead and start looting, heee heee. Hah, hrumph. Hahahahha. Ye gods, what is th-hahahahhahahah!"
They say there is no rose without a thorn, but this was somewhat excessive.
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: Dicen que no hay rosa sin espina, pero esto fue algo excesivo.

character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_original: "See if this was in those plaques of yours. Which I'm taking."
character_trait_levels_colour_text_teb_t.value_translated: "A ver si esto estaba en esas placas tuyas. Que me lo llevo".

character_trait_levels_explanation_text_.value_translated: Has derrotado a El Cadavo, otra vez
El Cadavo derrotó a el Señor Mazdamundi

character_trait_levels_onscreen_name_teb.value_translated: A la tercera va la vencida

could be Pavona for plot reasons, TBD.key: could be Pavona for plot reasons, TBD

cultures_frontend_description_mixer_teb_.value_original: The so-called Southern Realms stretch from the messy Border Princes to Estalia, and into their sparse colonies in the New World. These human realms may not be as powerful, or remotely as united as the Empire, but some of their parts are uniquely wealthy and dynamic. Alternatively, they are also substantially corrupt and pathologically quarrelsome. \\n\\nWhile the Border Princes are the refuge of any misfit living there for their sins, or leaving other regions in desperation, the City-States of Tilea are particularly famous for their wealth and for some of the best and most professional human warriors to ever grace the mercenary markets of the Old World. This is related to the presence of the Myrmidian cults, the strongest faith in the south, one that favours equally mercy, wisdom and tactical acumen.
cultures_frontend_description_mixer_teb_.value_translated: Los llamados Reinos del Sur se extienden desde los desordenados Príncipes Fronterisos hasta Estalia, pasando por sus escasas colonias en el Nuevo Mundo. Puede que estos reinos humanos no sean tan poderosos ni estén ni remotamente tan unidos como el Imperio, pero algunas de sus partes son singularmente ricas y dinámicas. Alternativamente, también son sustancialmente corruptos y patológicamente pendencieros. \\Mientras que los Príncipes Fronterizos son el refugio de cualquier inadaptado que viva allí por sus pecados, o que abandone otras regiones desesperado, las Ciudades-Estado de Tilea son particularmente famosas por su riqueza y por algunos de los mejores y más profesionales guerreros humanos que jamás hayan honrado los mercados mercenarios del Viejo Mundo. Esto está relacionado con la presencia de los cultos mirmidianos, la fe más fuerte del sur, que favorece por igual la misericordia, la sabiduría y la perspicacia táctica.

cultures_subcultures_battle_playstyle_de.value_original: The Southern Realms offer the rosters of Tilea, Estalia, Border Princes and New World Colonies, each with their own peculiarities. \\nAs a whole, the Southern Realms offer good infantry and cavalry, some being the best the human race has to offer, including a large pool of Regiments of Renown. However, they lack in monsters and expensive machinery compared to other races, and rely on combined arms to neutralize the biggest threats.
cultures_subcultures_battle_playstyle_de.value_translated: Los Reinos del Sur ofrecen las listas de Tilea, Estalia, Reinos Fronterizos y Colonias del Nuevo Mundo, cada una con sus propias peculiaridades. \\En conjunto, los Reinos del Sur ofrecen buena infantería y caballería, algunas de las mejores que la raza humana puede ofrecer, incluyendo un gran número de Regimientos de Renombre. Sin embargo, carecen de monstruos y maquinaria costosa en comparación con otras razas, y confían en las armas combinadas para neutralizar las mayores amenazas.

dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_original: Centuries ago, the Order of Nahmud retrieved scrolls that could have been important texts concerning the Dark Maiden or her friend, Holy Myrmidia herself. Allegedly, any attempt to translate the texts was in vain until an elven guest managed the deed and suffered a deadly and unlikely accident for it. The issue has resurfaced and rumours are already circulating about the alleged secrets of the scrolls. Reports mention whispers musing the concept that Holy Myrmidia was actually an Elf, or even worse, an Arabyan! \\n\\n What would you have us do about the matter?
dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_translated: Hace siglos, la Orden de Nahmud recuperó unos pergaminos que podrían haber sido textos importantes relativos a la Doncella Oscura o a su amiga, la mismísima Santa Myrmidia. Supuestamente, cualquier intento de traducir los textos fue en vano hasta que un invitado elfo logró la hazaña y sufrió un mortal e improbable accidente por ello. El asunto ha resurgido y ya circulan rumores sobre los supuestos secretos de los pergaminos. Los informes mencionan susurros que barajan el concepto de que la Santa Myrmidia era en realidad una elfa, o peor aún, ¡una arabiga! \\¿Qué quieres que hagamos al respecto?

dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_original: We have reports of a hedge wizard operating in the area. He seems to be keeping to himself, and yet is known to help the local populace in everyday issues. He could be a useful asset for our troops, but the northeners often execute these untrained mages on sight for fear of them turning into some horror or the other. What would you choose?
dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_translated: Tenemos informes de un mago de los setos que opera en la zona. Parece reservado, pero se sabe que ayuda a la población local en asuntos cotidianos. Podría ser un activo útil para nuestras tropas, pero los norteños a menudo ejecutan a estos magos sin entrenamiento en el acto por temor a que se conviertan en algún horror u otro. ¿Qué elegirías?

dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_original: One of the local pasta recipes is a traditional staple. However, it is just as traditional for people, from the family mother to the renowned cook, to squabble over one particular ingredient being used, replaced or not. The issue has come up again and there have been fights from street to mansion level. What would you tell people to settle this down, at least for the moment?
dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_translated: Una de las recetas locales de pasta es un alimento básico tradicional. Sin embargo, es igual de tradicional que la gente, desde la madre de familia hasta el cocinero de renombre, se pelee por un ingrediente concreto que se utiliza, se sustituye o no. El tema ha vuelto a surgir y ha habido peleas desde la calle hasta a nivel de mansión. ¿Qué le diría a la gente para calmar los ánimos, al menos de momento?

dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_original: One of the artists under your patronage found a handful of sketches that look distinctly Leonardo da Miragliano-esque. If anything, they are written in a thick spidery and mirrored script, every page full to the edge of further notes and sketches. An emissary from Altdorf has heard of the rumours and seems eager to get the notes to his Emperor.
dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_translated: Uno de los artistas bajo tu patrocinio encontró un puñado de bocetos que parecen claramente Leonardo da Miragliano. En todo caso, están escritos en una gruesa letra de araña y espejada, cada página llena hasta el borde de más notas y bocetos. Un emisario de Altdorf se ha enterado de los rumores y parece ansioso por hacer llegar las notas a su Emperador.

dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_original: We have estabilished a satisfactory trade network with our neighbours. What matters now is how we continue handling our trade markets.
dilemmas_localised_description_teb_dilem.value_translated: Hemos establecido una red comercial satisfactoria con nuestros vecinos. Lo que importa ahora es cómo seguimos gestionando nuestros mercados comerciales.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: An assembly of mercenary companies have set up camp here. Any army within its circle of influence will be able to recruit units from the camp.

Each company has decided the fate of their respective prisoners. The troops seem happy with the results and the extra loot acquired. An enemy noble has been seen running clothed in nothing but a ragged sack.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Cada compañía ha decidido el destino de sus respectivos prisioneros. Las tropas parecen contentas con los resultados y el botín extra adquirido. Se ha visto correr a un noble enemigo vestido únicamente con un saco harapiento.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Recent events made the elites of our nation less enthusiastic.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Los recientes acontecimientos han desanimado a las élites de nuestra nación.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: "I mean, sir, have you ever seen pulleys being used like this? There are fourteen vectors all contributing to an upward surge plus the- yes sir, I shall shut up immediately."
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: "Señor, ¿alguna vez ha visto poleas usadas así? Hay catorce vectores contribuyendo todos a un impulso ascendente más el... sí señor, me callaré inmediatamente".

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: There could be so much to learn from someone who could design a breath-taking portrait in the same page as a new ballista prototype and... an automated fork?
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Hay tanto que aprender de alguien capaz de diseñar un retrato impresionante en la misma página que un nuevo prototipo de balista y... ¿un tenedor automatizado?

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Princes and Lords will keep the wheel rolling for you, while they also line their own pockets. Their assets may however be at your disposal, should you need them.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Los Príncipes y Señores mantendrán la rueda en marcha para ti, mientras ellos también se llenan los bolsillos. No obstante, sus activos pueden estar a tu disposición si los necesitas.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: The neighbours will be happy that we're pointing our goods at them and not our troops. Besides, nobody's deaf to the clinking of money.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Los vecinos se alegrarán de que les apuntemos con nuestros bienes y no con nuestras tropas. Además, nadie está sordo al tintineo del dinero.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: You have successfully found, willingly or not, the living and muttering remains of a former king of Magritta. Rejoice!
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Has encontrado con éxito, voluntariamente o no, los restos vivientes y murmurantes de un antiguo Rey de Magritta. ¡Alégrate!

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Through innovative tactics and personal hard work, any fortification will be in Borgio's hands by snack time. Dinner, tops.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Mediante tácticas innovadoras y trabajo personal, cualquier fortificación estará en manos de Borgio a la hora de la merienda. La cena, como mucho.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Driven by greed, spirit of adventure, debts or all of the above, southerner colonists and warriors are eager to face the New World.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Impulsados por la codicia, el espíritu de aventura, las deudas o todo lo anterior, los colonos y guerreros sureños están ansiosos por enfrentarse al Nuevo Mundo.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: A commercial and mercenary foothold in Cathay that would make Ricco and Robbio proud and jealous.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Un punto de apoyo comercial y mercenario en Catai que haría que Ricco y Robbio se sintieran orgullosos y celosos.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Led by the best navigator in the Southern Realms, Colombo's men will savour the New World virtually unimpended, potentially with the unique friendship of the local Lizardmen.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Dirigidos por el mejor navegante de los Reinos del Sur, los hombres de Colombo saborearán el Nuevo Mundo prácticamente sin depender de nadie, potencialmente con la amistad única de los Hombres Lagarto locales.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Colombo's new enterprise puts together the experience of his Trantian entrepreneurs, Lizardmen contacts and the heavily-armed support of Myrmidian cults.
Gashnag's benevolent rule encourages a stable kingdom, but his own nature is a tricky matter.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: El gobierno benevolente de Gashnag fomenta un reino estable, pero su propia naturaleza es un asunto peliagudo.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: The Prince of Akendorf is a strong guide with many challenges around and ahead of him.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: El Príncipe de Akendorf es un guía fuerte con muchos retos a su alrededor y por delante.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Luccini may be traditionally led by eccentric and slightly-inbred Princes, but it prides itself with what is likely the best army of Tilea, a famed fleet and a luxurious lifestyle.
The forced exile from the razed homecity of Pavona determines that Lucrezzia's qualities and abilities must ensure new possibilities.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: El exilio forzoso de la arrasada ciudad natal de Pavona determina que las cualidades y habilidades de Lucrezzia deban asegurar nuevas posibilidades.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Commoners of Estalia who are far away from the king's collectors consider themselves lucky.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Los plebeyos de Estalia que se encuentran lejos de los recaudadores del rey se consideran afortunados.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: Through innovative tactics and personal hard work, any fortification will be in Borgio's hands by snack time. Dinner, tops.
Driven by greed, spirit of adventure, debts or all of the above, southerner colonists and warriors are eager to face the New World.
A commercial and mercenary foothold in Cathay that would make Ricco and Robbio proud and jealous.
Led by the best navigator in the Southern Realms, Colombo's men will savour the New World virtually unimpended, potentially with the unique friendship of the local Lizardmen.
Colombo's new enterprise puts together the experience of his Trantian entrepreneurs, Lizardmen contacts and the heavily-armed support of Myrmidian cults.
Gashnag's benevolent rule encourages a stable kingdom, but his own nature is a tricky matter.
The Prince of Akendorf is a strong guide with many challenges around and ahead of him.
Luccini may be traditionally led by eccentric and slightly-inbred Princes, but it prides itself with what is likely the best army of Tilea, a famed fleet and a luxurious lifestyle.
The forced exile from the razed homecity of Pavona determines that Lucrezzia's qualities and abilities must ensure new possibilities.
Commoners of Estalia who are far away from the king's collectors consider themselves lucky.
Master Duellists can be recruited factionwide and with increased rank.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: El Contrato de Maestro Duellista no puede ser renovado.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: El contrato de Hechicero de Batalla no se puede renovar.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: The upcoming enterprises require masses. The Princes have agreed that drowning the common enemy in bodies is the reasonable strategy here, no matter the drop in average troop quality.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Las empresas que se avecinan requieren masas. Los Príncipes han acordado que ahogar al enemigo común en cadáveres es la estrategia razonable en este caso, sin importar el descenso de la calidad media de las tropas.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: The conflicts ahead require that the only troops fielded are going to be the very best the treasury can afford.
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Los conflictos que se avecinan requieren que las únicas tropas desplegadas sean las mejores que el tesoro pueda permitirse.

effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_original: With no visible threat or opportunities allegedly in sight, the Princes cut the costs and allow most of their captains to be hired elsewhere en masse. This brings huge savings, but until the lease and the gamble is over, the City-States are vulnerable...
effect_bundles_localised_description_teb.value_translated: Sin ninguna amenaza visible ni oportunidades supuestamente a la vista, los Príncipes recortan gastos y permiten que la mayoría de sus capitanes sean contratados en masa en otros lugares. Esto supone un gran ahorro, pero hasta que el arrendamiento y la apuesta terminen, las Ciudades-Estado son vulnerables...
