frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: [BETA]\\nTilean Prince Leonardo Catrazza is in the far east. After securing the Iron Dragon's partnership, he takes an aggressive bid on the spice route.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nEl príncipe tileano Leonardo Catrazza se encuentra en el lejano oriente. Tras conseguir la colaboración del Dragón de Hierro, se lanza a una agresiva puja por la ruta de las especias.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: [BETA]\\nValmir Gausser is a promising ruler in the Border Princes, one who may finally unite the lands at peace with the many nosy neighbours.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_border}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nValmir Gausser es un gobernante prometedor en los Reinos Fronterizos, uno que puede finalmente unir las tierras en paz con los muchos vecinos entrometidos.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_border}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: [BETA]\\nAn incognito Strigoi Prince ruling over his lands in the Border Princes, Gashnag is an intentionally-curated benevolent and protective presence.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_border}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nPríncipe Strigoi de incógnito que gobierna sus tierras en los Reinos Fronterizos, Gashnag es una presencia benévola y cuidadosamente protectora.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_border}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: [BETA]\\nLuccini is a city of eccentricity, opulence, and military traditions. All in the athletic grip of its current prince.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nLuccini es una ciudad de excentricidad, opulencia y tradiciones militares. Todo bajo el atlético control de su actual príncipe.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: [BETA]\\nThe eccentric Lupio Sunscryer, Prince of Magritta, believes in gold and himself. And gold is all around Estalia, if one is keen to reach for it.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_estalia}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nEl excéntrico Lupio Escrutasoles, príncipe de Magritta, cree en el oro y en sí mismo. Y el oro está por todas partes en Estalia, si uno tiene ganas de alcanzarlo.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_estalia}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: [BETA]\\nTilea is besieged by ratmen, pirates and greenskins. However, they didn't account for the return of the Besieger.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nTilea está asediada por hombres rata, piratas y pieles verdes. Sin embargo, no tuvieron en cuenta el regreso del Sitiador.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: While everything is absolutely and undeniably swell with his new city in the New World, Cadavo leads a diversifying expedition into Bretonnia, land of foolish - and rich - nobles who challenged him once too many.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_colonies}}

[BETA]\\nFamous navigator, marksman, diplomat and adventurer Marco Colombo is at the head of a joint venture and Myrmidian crusade in the exotic, though frigid, lands of Norsca.\\n[[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Merc-Myrmidian Expedition: hybrid roster with mercenary and cult units.
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nEl famoso navegante, tirador, diplomático y aventurero Marco Colombo está al frente de una empresa conjunta y de una cruzada myrmidiana en las exóticas, aunque gélidas, tierras de Norsca.\\n[[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Expedición mercenaria-myrmidiana: elenco híbrido con unidades de mercenarios y cultistas.

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: [BETA]\\nSorceress Lucrezzia Belladonna is a mistress of diplomacy, manipulation and discreet assassination.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: [BETA]\\nLa hechicera Lucrezzia Belladonna es una maestra de la diplomacia, la manipulación y el asesinato discreto.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: Ruthless Cadavo has his eye set on lizard gold, and his fame attracts many mercenaries and adventurers who desire a slice of the cake.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_colonies}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: El despiadado Cadavo ha puesto sus ojos en el oro de los lagartos, y su fama atrae a muchos mercenarios y aventureros que desean una parte del pastel.\n{tr:frontend_bullet_colonies}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: Valmir Gausser is a promising ruler in the Border Princes, one who may finally unite the lands at peace with the many nosy neighbours.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_border}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: Valmir Gausser es un gobernante prometedor en los Reinos Fronterizos, que puede unir finalmente las tierras en paz con los muchos vecinos entrometidos.

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: The eccentric Lupio Sunscryer, Prince of Magritta, believes in gold and himself. And gold is all around Estalia, if one is keen to reach for it.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_estalia}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: El excéntrico Lupio Escrutasoles, Príncipe de Magritta, cree en el oro y en sí mismo. Y el oro está por todas partes en Estalia, si uno está dispuesto a alcanzarlo.

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: Tilea is besieged by ratmen, pirates and greenskins. However, they didn't account for the return of the Besieger.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: Tilea está asediada por hombres rata, piratas y pieles verdes. Sin embargo, no contaban con el regreso del Sitiador.

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: Tilean Sorceress Lucrezzia Belladonna secured Bilbali as her new seat, and her arts of manipulation will serve her well in Estalia and beyond.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_estalia}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: La hechicera tileana Lucrezzia Belladonna se ha asegurado Bilbali como su nueva sede, y sus artes de manipulación le serán muy útiles en Estalia y más allá.

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: Tilean Prince Leonardo Catrazza is in the far east, securely straddled on the silk road. In the wake of Cathayan disorder, he secures Zhao Ming's partnership and uses his embassy as a trampoline for opportunities unseen before.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: El príncipe tileano Leonardo Catrazza se encuentra en el lejano oriente, seguro en la ruta de la seda. Tras los desórdenes catayanos, se asegura la asociación de Zhao Ming y utiliza su embajada como trampolín para oportunidades nunca antes vistas.\n{tr:frontend_bullet_tilea}}

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: Famous navigator, marksman, diplomat and adventurer Marco Colombo is once again in exotic lands to secure further wealth and fame.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_colonies}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: El famoso navegante, tirador, diplomático y aventurero Marco Colombo se encuentra de nuevo en tierras exóticas para asegurarse más riqueza y fama.

frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_original: An incognito Strigoi Prince ruling over his lands in the Border Princes, Gashnag is an intentionally-curated benevolent and protective presence.\\n{{tr:frontend_bullet_border}}
frontend_faction_leaders_frontend_descri.value_translated: Príncipe Strigoi de incógnito que gobierna sus tierras en los Reinos Fronterizos, Gashnag es una presencia benévola y protectora intencionada.\n{tr:frontend_bullet_border}}

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: Tilean is famous for many things, such as arts, mercenaries, cuisine and wealth. Leonardo Catrazza, away from the cumbersome presence of Borgio in Miragliano, has been investing in the silk road to export anything the Cathayans may be interested in, and ship back to Tilea anything that will sell dearly.

Although the dwellers of the Borderlands wouldn't care to admit it, the humans of this country are like a large, robust creeper. Centuries ago, human colonists and refugees started to built a new nation on the borders of the Old World. Anyone else would have been strangled between mountains and sea, between Dwarfs and Greenskins. Today, one of the many self-defined princes of these lands may have the potential to unite the many squabbling towns and clear out the many threats. Valmir Gausser distinguished himself as a solid warrior and commander in Araby, and can claim to have friends in both Bretonnia and Dwarfdom.

Heir to the Strigoi King Vorag Bloodytooth, Gashnag rules a small domain in the Border Princes. As opposed to his sire's aggressive and bloody tendencies, Gashnag has chosen a more peaceful and reclusive form of government, emulous to the empire of Ushoran, the very first of the Strigoi bloodline. The Black Prince, as he is rather affectionately known among his subjects, hides his true nature and personally protects the towns under his rule from incursions. In order to avoid unwanted attentions from feral Strigoi, jealous Von Carsteins or neighbouring Princes, Gashnag wears a heavy black cloak and multiple illusions, upholding a façade as a scarred but romantically heroic figure of selflessness.\\nGashnag is inclined to find and research Ushoran's secrets, lost in the Badlands, to augment his powers. However, he needs to decide whether to continue on that route or rush back to protect his princedom from encroaching Ogres.

Luccini is one of the most ancient human settlements in the Old World, and Lorenzo Lupo is, appropriately, a leader that seems born in ages past. Like many of his ancient bloodline, he is considered a bizarre and not completely sane individual; unlike many of his family, he carries his athletic body and the archaic weaponry of his forebears with extreme efficiency. And he must, for Luccini is again threatened by pirates, greenskins and ratmen.

While many of his descriptions include the words "gold-obsessed" and "deranged", Lupio Sunscryer also has the ambition necessary to fulfill Estalia's destiny. He has a score to settle, though, with his imaginary enemies in the Valley of Windmills. He has led an expedition there, attempting to rid the world of the wretched wooden monsters as they plot with their Ratmen allies.

The news about Borgio's death to a poisoned fork was greatly exaggerated. To the relief of his many followers, troops and allies, the Prince of Miragliano is back in business and ready to lead his hosts against the mounting threats to Tilea.

The legend of El Cadavo originates in Tilea, land of a thousand mercenary commanders. Cadavo was one of the most ruthless, and he was ultimately responsible for the origins of another story, that of the Alcatani Fellowship. Years later, Cadavo is still a leader of men, stubborn entrepreneur, founder of colonies, peerless warrior. Some say all those stories cannot possibly fit one lifetime...

Some people are positively restless. Marco Colombo, famous explorer, commander and thus politician from a Tilean point of view is back on the move. Even after becoming Prince of Trantio as a follow-up, and uniquely succeeding in securing the friendship of Lord Mazdamundi (or at least, non-hostility). Colombo is overseas again, this time having secured the strong-willed support of the Myrmidian cults and, most noticeably, in the inclement lands of Norsca. His knights in shining armour might be in it for righteous purposes, but Marco has his eyes on the unclaimed riches of this hellscape.

Lucrezzia Belladonna is the most beautiful lady in the Old World, at least according to those who aren't interested in getting on the bad side of devious plots and mysterious assassinations. From her current seat in florid Pavona, Lucrezzia survives seven influential but ultimately-disposable husbands and rules over a spidersilk net of subtle political dominance. However, one mistake, and many enemies might flock against her.

The legend of El Cadavo originates in Tilea, land of a thousand mercenary commanders. Cadavo was one of the most ruthless, and he was ultimately responsible for the origins of another story, that of the Alcatani Fellowship. Years later, Cadavo is still a leader of men, stubborn entrepreneur, founder of colonies, peerless warrior. Some say all those stories cannot possibly fit one lifetime...
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: La leyenda de El Cadavo tiene su origen en Tilea, tierra de mil comandantes mercenarios. Cadavo fue uno de los más despiadados, y a él se debe en última instancia el origen de otra historia, la de la Hermandad Alcatani. Años después, Cadavo sigue siendo líder de hombres, emprendedor obstinado, fundador de colonias, guerrero sin par. Hay quien dice que todas esas historias no caben en una vida...

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: Although the dwellers of the Borderlands wouldn't care to admit it, the humans of this country are like a large, robust creeper. Centuries ago, human colonists and refugees started to built a new nation on the borders of the Old World. Anyone else would have been strangled between mountains and sea, between Dwarfs and Greenskins. Today, one of the many self-defined princes of these lands may have the potential to unite the many squabbling towns and clear out the many threats. Valmir Gausser distinguished himself as a solid warrior and commander in Araby, and can claim to have friends in both Bretonnia and Dwarfdom.
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: Aunque a los habitantes de las Tierras Fronterizas no les gustaría admitirlo, los humanos de este país son como una enredadera grande y robusta. Hace siglos, colonos y refugiados humanos empezaron a construir una nueva nación en las fronteras del Viejo Mundo. Cualquier otro habría quedado estrangulado entre montañas y mares, entre Enanos y Pieles Verdes. Hoy, uno de los muchos príncipes autodefinidos de estas tierras puede tener el potencial para unir a los muchos pueblos en disputa y acabar con las muchas amenazas. Valmir Gausser se distinguió como un sólido guerrero y comandante en Arabia, y puede presumir de tener amigos tanto en Bretonia como en los dominos de los Enanos.

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: While many of his descriptions include the words "gold-obsessed" and "deranged", Lupio Sunscryer also has the ambition necessary to fulfill Estalia's destiny. As he readies his people for war, Lupio looks to the north and to the east; should his tercios encroach on Bretonnia or Tilea first? Closer to home, ratmen infest the fallen city of Tylos and the peninsula is ever threatened by unholy pirates and beasts of Chaos. It is by Myrmidia's will that Lupio will purge these abominations and cement Estalia as the foremost nation of men in the Old World.
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: Aunque muchas de sus descripciones incluyen las palabras "obsesionado con el oro" y "trastornado", Lupio Escrutasoles también tiene la ambición necesaria para cumplir el destino de Estalia. Mientras prepara a su pueblo para la guerra, Lupio mira al norte y al este: ¿deberían sus tercios invadir primero Bretonia o Tilea? Más cerca de casa, los hombres rata infestan la ciudad caída de Tylos y la península está siempre amenazada por piratas impíos y bestias del Caos. Por voluntad de Myrmidia, Lupio purgará estas abominaciones y cimentará Estalia como la principal nación de hombres del Viejo Mundo.

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: The news about Borgio's death to a poisoned fork was greatly exaggerated. To the relief of his many followers, troops and allies, the Prince of Miragliano is back in business and ready to lead his hosts against the mounting threats to Tilea.
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: Las noticias sobre la muerte de Borgio a causa de un tenedor envenenado fueron muy exageradas. Para alivio de sus numerosos seguidores, tropas y aliados, el Príncipe de Miragliano ha vuelto a la carga y está listo para liderar a sus huestes contra las crecientes amenazas que se ciernen sobre Tilea.

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: The city-state of Pavona has been mostly destroyed. Not by other Tileans as so many times it has been threatened, but by the greenskin beasts from the mountains. Lucrezzia is not only the most beautiful woman in the Old World, or so they say, but also a resourceful woman. If the old ally, Prince Borgio, cannot help her in vengeance, she can surely manipulate her way into Estalia for a new secure base.
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: La ciudad-estado de Pavona ha sido destruida en su mayor parte. No por otros tileanos como tantas veces se ha visto amenazada, sino por las bestias pielesverdes de las montañas. Lucrezzia no sólo es la mujer más bella del Viejo Mundo, o eso dicen, sino también una mujer de recursos. Si el viejo aliado, el príncipe Borgio, no puede ayudarla en la venganza, seguro que puede manipular su camino hacia Estalia para conseguir una nueva base segura.

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: Tilean is famous for many things, such as arts, mercenaries, cuisine and wealth. Leonardo Catrazza, away from the cumbersome presence of Borgio in Miragliano, has been investing in the silk road to export anything the Cathayans may be interested in, and ship back to Tilea anything that will sell dearly. New opportunities arise in Cathay, as the draconic rulers struggle for control, and Leonardo may very well profit from his partnership with the Iron Dragon in ways that neither of the two could foresee.
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: Tilea es famosa por muchas cosas, como las artes, los mercenarios, la cocina y la riqueza. Leonardo Catrazza, lejos de la engorrosa presencia de Borgio en Miragliano, ha estado invirtiendo en la ruta de la seda para exportar cualquier cosa que pueda interesar a los catayanos, y enviar de vuelta a Tilea todo lo que se venda caro. En Catai surgen nuevas oportunidades, ya que los gobernantes dracónicos luchan por el control, y Leonardo podría beneficiarse de su asociación con el Dragón de Hierro de formas que ninguno de los dos podría prever.

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: Some people are positively restless. Marco Colombo, famous explorer, commander and thus politician from a Tilean point of view is back on the move. Even after becoming Prince of Trantio as a follow-up, and uniquely succeeding in securing the friendship of Lord Mazdamundi (or at least, non-hostility). Colombo is overseas again, bringing his experience and wealth to bear on the frontier, paid exorbitantly by the Slann to destroy as many corsairs and pirates as possible.
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: Algunas personas están positivamente inquietas. Marco Colombo, famoso explorador, comandante y, por tanto, político desde el punto de vista tileano, ha vuelto a la carga. Incluso después de haberse convertido en Príncipe de Trantio como continuación, y de haber conseguido la amistad de Lord Mazdamundi (o al menos, la no hostilidad). Colombo está de nuevo en ultramar, aportando su experiencia y riqueza a la frontera, pagado exorbitantemente por los Slann para destruir a tantos corsarios y piratas como sea posible.

frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_original: Heir to the Strigoi King Vorag Bloodytooth, Gashnag rules a small domain in the Border Princes. As opposed to his sire's aggressive and bloody tendencies, Gashnag has chosen a more peaceful and reclusive form of government, emulous to the empire of Ushoran, the very first of the Strigoi bloodline. The Black Prince, as he is rather affectionately known among his subjects, hides his true nature and personally protects the towns under his rule from incursions. In order to avoid unwanted attentions from feral Strigoi, jealous Von Carsteins or neighbouring Princes, Gashnag wears a heavy black cloak and multiple illusions, upholding a façade as a scarred but romantically heroic figure of selflessness.\\nGashnag is inclined to find and research Ushoran's secrets, lost in the Badlands, to augment his powers. However, he needs to decide whether to continue on that route or rush back to protect his princedom from encroaching Ogres.
frontend_faction_leaders_loading_screen_.value_translated: Heredero del rey strigoi Vorag Diente Sangriento, Gashnag gobierna un pequeño reino en los Príncipes Fronterizos. Frente a las tendencias agresivas y sangrientas de su progenitor, Gashnag ha elegido una forma de gobierno más pacífica y solitaria, emulando al imperio de Ushoran, el primero de la estirpe Strigoi. El Príncipe Negro, como se le conoce cariñosamente entre sus súbditos, oculta su verdadera naturaleza y protege personalmente de las incursiones a las ciudades bajo su dominio. Para evitar las atenciones no deseadas de Strigoi salvajes, Von Carstein celosos o Príncipes vecinos, Gashnag lleva una pesada capa negra y múltiples ilusiones, manteniendo una fachada de figura desinteresada, cicatrizada pero románticamente heroica.\nGashnag se inclina por encontrar e investigar los secretos de Ushoran, perdidos en las Tierras Yermas, para aumentar sus poderes. Sin embargo, tiene que decidir si sigue por ese camino o vuelve corriendo para proteger su principado de los Ogros invasores.

frontend_factions_localised_mechanics_mi.value_original: [[img:bullet_chs_awaken]][[/img]]Tilea, Estalia, Border Princes and New World Colonies: four subgroups with roster and mechanic variations, each with their own challenges and advantages.||[[img:bullet_treasury]][[/img]]Plutocracy: strong economy can sustain vast expenses, finance political maneuvers and fuel expensive collections of exotic items.||[[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Mercenary and Border Armies: rosters of local and foreign infantry and cavalry, favouring combined arms, Regiments of Renown and specialist heroes over complicated contraptions. Experienced units get additional benefits.
frontend_factions_localised_mechanics_mi.value_translated: [[img:bullet_chs_awaken]][[/img]]Tilea, Estalia, Reinos Fronterizos y Colonias del Nuevo Mundo: cuatro subgrupos con un listado de unidades y variaciones mecánicas, cada una con sus propios retos y ventajas.||[[img:bullet_treasury]][[/img]]Plutocracia: una economía fuerte puede mantener grandes gastos, financiar maniobras políticas y alimentar costosas colecciones de objetos exóticos.||[[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Ejércitos mercenarios y fronterizos: listado de unidades de infantería y caballería local y extranjera, que favorecen las armas combinadas, los Regimientos de Renombre y los héroes especialistas frente a complicados artilugios. Las unidades experimentadas obtienen ventajas adicionales.

frontend_factions_localised_playstyle_wh.value_original: The Border Princes may not have the resources or the manpower of the Empire, and yet the heirs of the colonist endure the daily struggle offered by irreducible neighbours.
frontend_factions_localised_playstyle_wh.value_translated: Puede que los Príncipes de la Frontera no dispongan de los recursos ni de la mano de obra del Imperio, y sin embargo los herederos del colono soportan la lucha diaria que ofrecen unos vecinos irreductibles.

frontend_factions_localised_playstyle_wh.value_original: Estalia is a nation projected outwards, like the peninsula that hosts it. Beyond an immense ocean lies Lustria and its well-defended riches. Eastwards, the Bretonnians and yes, the Tileans. Perhaps it is time for the might of Estalia to raise its head.
frontend_factions_localised_playstyle_wh.value_translated: Estalia es una nación proyectada hacia el exterior, como la península que la acoge. Más allá de un inmenso océano se encuentra Lustria y sus riquezas bien defendidas. Hacia el este, los bretonianos y sí, los tileanos. Tal vez haya llegado el momento de que el poder de Estalia levante cabeza.

frontend_factions_localised_playstyle_wh.value_original: Tilea sits between its rival, Estalia, the Dwarfs of the Vaults, the troubled Border Princes and a lunatic sea infested by pirates, undead, corsairs and even orcish pirates. The Princes of Tilea are however sitting on a pile of wealth, efficient warriors and inventive minds...
frontend_factions_localised_playstyle_wh.value_translated: Tilea se encuentra entre su rival, Estalia, los Enanos de las Bóvedas, los problemáticos Príncipes de la Frontera y un mar lunático infestado de piratas, muertos vivientes, corsarios e incluso piratas orcos. Sin embargo, los Príncipes de Tilea están sentados sobre un montón de riquezas, guerreros eficientes y mentes inventivas...

incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_original: Most informed parts have been silenced, one way or another. The resolution didn't go unnoticed, and some groups have become more grim and less enthusiastic.
incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_translated: La mayoría de las partes informadas han sido silenciadas, de un modo u otro. La resolución no pasó desapercibida, y algunos grupos se han vuelto más sombríos y menos entusiastas.

incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_original: Rumours of this kind are mostly part of a healthy and chatty society. The noisiest reaction came from two Magrittan priests, whose flaming row was eventually settled by their colleagues, with a club.
incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_translated: Los rumores de este tipo suelen formar parte de una sociedad sana y parlanchina. La reacción más ruidosa provino de dos sacerdotes magritanos, cuya encendida disputa acabaron zanjando sus colegas a garrotazos.

incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_original: We have proven to be the better person compared to the sigmarite northeners, who would torch a city down at the merest hint of discussion. A vocal minority in the populace was outraged by the notion that Myrmidia could be nothing but a pureblooded Estalian (or Tilean, depending on whom you ask), which may cause some noise. \\nHowever, part of the Court of Lothern was pleasantly surprised by our transparence, which may mean trade.
incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_translated: Hemos demostrado ser la mejor persona en comparación con los norteños sigmaritas, que incendiarían una ciudad al menor atisbo de discusión. Una minoría ruidosa de la población se indignó ante la idea de que Myrmidia no podía ser más que una estaliana de sangre pura (o tileana, según a quién preguntes), lo que puede causar algo de ruido. \\Sin embargo, parte de la Corte de Lothern quedó gratamente sorprendida por nuestra transparencia, lo que puede significar comercio.

incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_original: A Knight of the Order of the Eagle offered to personally check on the subject and take action if needed. As it turns out, the man was only a scholar gone-hermit that occasionally felt like helping a neighbour. However, the Templar claims to have actually found a distinct but deranged person on the way back to the capital. The man bore clear signs of ruinous temptation and was skewered while busy eating snails.
incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_translated: Un Caballero de la Orden del Águila se ofreció a comprobar personalmente el estado del sujeto y tomar medidas si era necesario. Resulta que el hombre no era más que un erudito ido-ermitaño al que de vez en cuando le apetecía ayudar a un vecino. Sin embargo, el templario afirma haber encontrado a una persona distinta pero trastornada en el camino de vuelta a la capital. El hombre mostraba claros signos de ruinosa tentación y fue ensartado mientras estaba ocupado comiendo caracoles.

incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_original: The man was offered to join your services on probation. He was also proven to be a stable and promising wizard and is awaiting your orders.
incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_translated: Al hombre se le ofreció unirse a sus servicios en periodo de prueba. También se ha demostrado que es un mago estable y prometedor y está esperando tus órdenes.

incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_original: Let's face it, Tileans enjoy these squabbles too much to let go. We're better off ignoring them until they settle down again.
incidents_localised_description_teb_dile.value_translated: Admitámoslo, los tileanos disfrutan demasiado con estas disputas como para dejarlas pasar. Es mejor ignorarlas hasta que vuelvan a calmarse.

incidents_localised_description_teb_inci.value_original: One of your Captains has been struck by one of those wretched rats' guns. The field surgeon was quick to realize the leg had to be amputated, and called for a dozen assistants to keep the big man down while he operated. The Captain refused and grabbed a candle to make light for the surgeon himself. The warrior is recovering, but the tale of his steely resolve spread like the smell of ale around the country, inebriating soldiers with similar bravery.
incidents_localised_description_teb_inci.value_translated: Uno de tus capitanes ha sido alcanzado por una de las armas de esas desdichadas ratas. El cirujano de campaña no tardó en darse cuenta de que había que amputarle la pierna y llamó a una docena de ayudantes para que mantuvieran al grandullón en el suelo mientras lo operaba. El capitán se negó y cogió una vela para alumbrar al cirujano. El guerrero se está recuperando, pero la historia de su férrea determinación se extendió como el olor de la cerveza por todo el país, embriagando a los soldados con una valentía similar.

incidents_localised_description_teb_inci.value_original: Bretonnians formally despise mercenaries and everything that goes with them. However, they are human like anybody else and even they will dance loops around holes in their chivalric codes. \\nAn emissary from a Dukedom absolutely *didn't* ask us for good soldiers to pose as shepherds, and we *didn't* get a nice cut over the contract for a company headed north, positively *not* to watch the border against greenskin incursions. We *didn't* have to provide the one sheep they will legally protect, either. \\n\\nSheesh.
incidents_localised_description_teb_inci.value_translated: Los bretones desprecian formalmente a los mercenarios y todo lo que les acompaña. Sin embargo, son humanos como cualquier otro e incluso ellos bailarán bucles en torno a los agujeros de sus códigos caballerescos. \\Un emisario de un Ducado no nos pidió en absoluto buenos soldados para que se hicieran pasar por pastores, y no recibimos una buena tajada por el contrato de una compañía que se dirigía al norte, en absoluto para vigilar la frontera contra las incursiones pielesverdes. Tampoco tuvimos que proporcionarles la única oveja que protegerán legalmente. \\Jeje.

incidents_localised_description_teb_inci.value_original: One of your rivals has been found dead, one neat sword jab wound in his chest and the rictus of someone who’s seen the visage of death itself. Nearby, a scrap of paper with a ‘V’ jotted in refined penmanship and the drawing of a wasp. Parts of his assets could be claimed for your use.
incidents_localised_description_teb_inci.value_translated: Uno de tus rivales ha sido encontrado muerto, con una certera herida de espada en el pecho y el rictus de alguien que ha visto el rostro de la mismísima muerte. Cerca, un trozo de papel con una "V" anotada con refinada caligrafía y el dibujo de una avispa. Partes de su patrimonio podrían reclamarse para su uso.

incidents_localised_description_teb_spaw.value_original: The Cult of Myrmidia is watching your actions with benevolence, and templars are eager to fight at your side.
incidents_localised_description_teb_spaw.value_translated: El Culto de Myrmidia observa tus acciones con benevolencia, y los templarios están deseosos de luchar a tu lado.

incidents_localised_title_teb_incident_c.value_translated: Cirugía a la luz de las velas

kislev.value_original: is in zzz loc for compatibility
kislev.value_translated: is in zzz loc for compatibility

land_units_onscreen_name_teb_asarnil.value_translated: Asarnil, el Señor de los Dragones

land_units_onscreen_name_teb_besiegers.value_translated: Ballesteros de Asedio de Braganza (Ballesteros con Pavés)

land_units_onscreen_name_teb_muktar.value_translated: Perros del Desierto de Al Muktar

land_units_onscreen_name_teb_roc_kotss.value_original: Knights of the Starry Shield (Knights of the Righteous Spear)
land_units_onscreen_name_teb_roc_kotss.value_translated: Caballeros del Escudo Estrellado (Caballeros de la Lanza Justiciera)

land_units_onscreen_name_teb_roc_monteca.value_original: Knights Forlorn of Monte Castello (Knights Encarmine)
land_units_onscreen_name_teb_roc_monteca.value_translated: Caballeros Desamparados de Monte Castello (Caballeros Encarnados)

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_al.value_original: Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo, marching through the land/ Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo, with his honest band/ Feared by the greedy/ Loved by the needy/ Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo!
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_al.value_translated: Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo, marchando por la tierra/ Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo, con su honesta banda/ Temido por los codiciosos/ Amado por los necesitados/ ¡Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo, Rod-rigo!

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_am.value_original: The warrior sisterhood of Lustria hasn't really grasped the fine concept of mercenary service. To them, their hirer is just as weak as the target they have crushed...
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_am.value_translated: La hermandad guerrera de Lustria no ha comprendido realmente el fino concepto del servicio mercenario. Para ellos, su contratante es tan débil como el objetivo que han aplastado...

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_be.value_original: An unbeaten regiment forged by Borgio's exploits, the mere sight of the Besiegers in their heavy plate is enough to make surrender an option. "Invincibility at no extra charge."
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_be.value_translated: Un regimiento invicto forjado por las hazañas de Borgio, la mera visión de los sitiadores en sus pesadas placas es suficiente para hacer de la rendición una opción. "Invencibilidad sin coste adicional".

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_bo.value_original: To the sufficiently shrewd and tough, an Orc is just another prey.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_bo.value_translated: Para los suficientemente astutos y duros, un Orco es sólo otra presa.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_bw.value_original: Sitting in a shade of grey between Order of the Eagle and Estalian Inquisition, the Black Watch is made of the most fanatical and stubborn among knightly aristocracy.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_bw.value_translated: Situada en un tono gris entre la Orden del Águila y la Inquisición Estaliana, la Guardia Negra está formada por los más fanáticos y testarudos entre la aristocracia caballeresca.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ca.value_original: Experienced and well-protected, the Carabiniers have their muskets always pointed in the most dangerous blindside of the enemy.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ca.value_translated: Experimentados y bien protegidos, los carabineros tienen sus mosquetes siempre apuntando al flanco ciego más peligroso del enemigo.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_original: The fellow human is hardly worrisome when one has faced murderous lizardmen in Lustria.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_translated: El prójimo apenas preocupa cuando uno se ha enfrentado a asesinos hombres lagarto en Lustria.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_original: Good horses and fine steel moving fast on the battlefield.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_translated: Buenos caballos y fino acero que se mueven con rapidez en el campo de batalla.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_original: These hardy mercenaries have learned how to best deal harm unpunished.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_translated: Estos rudos mercenarios han aprendido a repartir daño de la mejor manera impune.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_original: A reliable force of veterans in heavy armour and the best handguns.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_co.value_translated: Una fuerza fiable de veteranos con armaduras pesadas y las mejores pistolas.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_cu.value_original: In a parody of his former mercenary career, Richter Kreugar is cursed to live as an undead, to be slain in battle only to rise again in the morning. So he marches on, with his silent regiment of undead companions...
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_cu.value_translated: En una parodia de su antigua carrera de mercenario, Richter Kreugar está maldito a vivir como un no muerto, a ser asesinado en batalla sólo para resucitar por la mañana. Así que sigue adelante, con su silencioso regimiento de compañeros no muertos...

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_en.value_original: Ostentatious and lethal with their red enamelled armour and peculiar dual-wielding techniques, the Knights Encarmine are a spoiled fury on the battlefield.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_en.value_translated: Ostentosos y letales con sus armaduras esmaltadas en rojo y sus peculiares técnicas de doble empuñadura, los Caballeros Encarminados son una furia consentida en el campo de batalla.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_fr.value_original: Wealthy horsemen fighting in the well-known Bretonnian style.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_fr.value_translated: Ricos jinetes que luchan al conocido estilo bretoniano.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ko.value_original: The Order of the Eagle is the armed protector of Myrmidia on the battlefield.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ko.value_translated: La Orden del Águila es el protector armado de Myrmidia en el campo de batalla.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_le.value_original: Exiled guardians of a sacred shrine, the Leopards always send back everything they earned. Taking out necessary expenses such as fine wine, silk shirts and pasta sauce.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_le.value_translated: Guardianes exiliados de un santuario sagrado, los Leopardos siempre devuelven todo lo que ganan. Quitando gastos necesarios como vino fino, camisas de seda y salsa para pasta.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_li.value_original: Smaller, mobile cannons can be instrumental in advanced tactics.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_li.value_translated: Los cañones más pequeños y móviles pueden ser decisivos en las tácticas avanzadas.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ma.value_original: Even amongst fellow Dark Elves, Mengil and his merry band would be considered excessively sanguinary. Truly, one must be properly desperate to hire such a company of heavily armed cannibals.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ma.value_translated: Incluso entre los Elfos Oscuros, Mengil y su alegre banda serían considerados excesivamente sanguinarios. Verdaderamente, hay que estar muy desesperado para contratar a semejante compañía de caníbales fuertemente armados.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ma.value_original: Each trooper in Maximilian Damark's company must get a bull's eye on a coin at 300 paces to demonstrate their skill. It doesn't take a genius to guess what they can do in battle.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ma.value_translated: Cada soldado de la compañía de Maximilian Damark debe hacer diana en una moneda a 300 pasos para demostrar su habilidad. No hace falta ser un genio para adivinar lo que pueden hacer en la batalla.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mi.value_original: Commoners armed with bows have any chance to help against the incursions from the Badlands.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mi.value_translated: Los plebeyos armados con arcos tienen alguna posibilidad de ayudar contra las incursiones de las Tierras Baldías.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mi.value_original: Well-equipped and hand-picked by the mercenary prince Sven Carlsson, these cavalrymen are a solid force.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mi.value_translated: Bien equipados y elegidos a dedo por el príncipe mercenario Sven Carlsson, estos soldados de caballería son una fuerza sólida.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mo.value_original: Big swords can help in cutting the teeth of a pikeline.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mo.value_translated: Las grandes espadas pueden ayudar a cortar los dientes de un piquero.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mu.value_original: Out of fate, prophecies and curses ride the Desert Dogs into everybody else's nightmares of blood and sand.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_mu.value_translated: Del destino, profecías y maldiciones cabalgan los Perros del Desierto hacia las pesadillas de sangre y arena de todos los demás.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_no.value_original: The Condottieri's own relatives may make up their bodyguard or crack unit.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_no.value_translated: Los propios familiares de los Condottieri pueden formar parte de su escolta o unidad de choque.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_or.value_original: After the loss of the monastery of Saint Origo in the heathen lands, the "Frothers" crusade with sweet abandon under blood-red banners. "Only the Sword Purifies."
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_or.value_translated: Tras la pérdida del monasterio de San Origo en tierras paganas, los "Frothers" cruzan con dulce abandono bajo estandartes rojo sangre. "Sólo la Espada Purifica".

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_pa.value_original: Spreading words of encouragement and promises of higher salary, the Paymaster makes sure the hired fighters don't get too hesitant.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_pa.value_translated: Repartiendo palabras de ánimo y promesas de un salario más alto, el Pagador se asegura de que los combatientes contratados no duden demasiado.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_pi.value_original: Clad in heavy armour, a formation of these pikemen is a deadly hedgehog pointed at the enemy.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_pi.value_translated: Vestidos con armadura pesada, una formación de estos piqueros es un erizo mortal apuntando al enemigo.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_pi.value_original: From desperation, hardships and tolling training grew that regiment capable of besting Sauri and Vampires alike by pike, sword and crossbow. "Trained in Lustria", in fact.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_pi.value_translated: De la desesperación, las penurias y el agotador entrenamiento surgió aquel regimiento capaz de vencer a Sauri y Vampiros por igual a golpe de pica, espada y ballesta. "Entrenados en Lustria", de hecho.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_re.value_original: Generals - and treasurers - need the best protection possible.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_re.value_translated: Los generales -y los tesoreros- necesitan la mejor protección posible.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ri.value_original: Beneath the looks of rich kids going to war to show off their gems-encrusted armour, lies the hard truth of a regiment that has never lost a fight. Warcry: "Liberty! Equity! Liquidity!"
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ri.value_translated: Bajo la apariencia de niños ricos que van a la guerra a lucir sus armaduras con incrustaciones de piedras preciosas, se esconde la dura verdad de un regimiento que nunca ha perdido un combate. Grito de guerra: "¡Libertad! ¡Equidad! Liquidez!"

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_sa.value_original: Why is the rum always gone?

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_sh.value_original: Dwarf-crafted gear and proud hearts bring forth the legacy of Khypris.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_sh.value_translated: Su equipo de artesanía enana y sus orgullosos corazones traen el legado de Khypris.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_sw.value_original: To these men, "fairplay" is just another one of those funny bretonnian kinds of cheese.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_sw.value_translated: Para estos hombres, el "juego limpio" no es más que otro de esos graciosos quesos bretonianos.

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ve.value_original: "They're barely even proper soldiers. No discipline, no uniforms and the worst breath you've ever smelt on anyone that wasn't an Ogre. So why do they fight like the personal guard of the Emperor?"
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ve.value_translated: "Apenas son soldados propiamente dichos. Sin disciplina, sin uniformes y con el peor aliento que hayas olido en alguien que no sea un Ogro. Entonces, ¿por qué luchan como la guardia personal del Emperador?"

loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ve.value_original: The swish of a cloak here, a twirl there, a dagger in the ribs of the bedazzled opponent. Determined, efficient, fashionable, like Vespero and his duellists.
loading_screen_quotes_description_teb_ve.value_translated: El movimiento de una capa aquí, un giro allá, una daga en las costillas del oponente deslumbrante. Decididos, eficientes, a la moda, como Vespero y sus duelistas.

loading_screen_quotes_title_teb_muktar.value_translated: Perros del desierto de Al Muktar

missions_OBJ_teb_eldaddio_req_02.value_original: Occupy, loot, sack or raze three settlements belonging to Tomb Kings.
missions_OBJ_teb_eldaddio_req_02.value_translated: Ocupa, saquea o arrasa tres asentamientos pertenecientes a los Reyes de las Tumbas.

missions_OBJ_teb_eldaddio_req_03.value_original: Have at least 5000 in your treasury to fund the completely voluntary but compulsory restoration efforts.
missions_OBJ_teb_eldaddio_req_03.value_translated: Ten al menos 5000 en tu tesorería para financiar los esfuerzos de restauración, completamente voluntarios pero obligatorios.

missions_localised_description_teb_eldad.value_original: A voice in your sleep, awkwardly familiar. A hint that you should investigate this region and make light.
missions_localised_description_teb_eldad.value_translated: Una voz en tu sueño, incómodamente familiar. Un indicio de que debes investigar esta región y hacer luz.

missions_localised_description_teb_eldad.value_original: Your spies and scholars find a subtle tread. A former king of Magritta, Eustaquio Sunscryer, disappeared in an expedition into the Land of the Dead, and yet there are rumours of something seething there. Furthermore, you weren't the only one hearing the resonating command.
missions_localised_description_teb_eldad.value_translated: Tus espías y eruditos encuentran una pisada sutil. Un antiguo rey de Magritta, Eustaquio Sunscryer, desapareció en una expedición a la Tierra de los Muertos, y sin embargo hay rumores de que algo bulle allí. Además, no fuiste el único que escuchó la resonante orden.

missions_localised_description_teb_eldad.value_original: The expedition is successful, but astonished. You have found Eustaquio. Dead, yet alive. Silenced, yet as arrogant and demanding as his worst depictions. You understand, from his disconcerting and looping explanation, that the local undead punished him for breaking into their sacred monuments, took his still beating heart and dipped the gold he coveted onto his body, till but a golden skeleton remained. \\n\\nThe Cult of Myrmidia is unsure on how to proceed, as Eustaquio seems to be possessed by nothing but himself.
missions_localised_description_teb_eldad.value_translated: La expedición tiene éxito, pero asombra. Has encontrado a Eustaquio. Muerto, pero vivo. Silenciado, pero tan arrogante y exigente como sus peores representaciones. Comprendes, por su desconcertante y en bucle explicación, que los muertos vivientes locales le castigaron por irrumpir en sus monumentos sagrados, le quitaron su corazón aún palpitante y sumergieron el oro que codiciaba en su cuerpo, hasta que sólo quedó un esqueleto dorado. \\El Culto de Myrmidia no está seguro de cómo proceder, ya que Eustaquio parece estar poseído por nada más que él mismo.

mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_original: Request or hire the aid of Lords and Heroes for your faction. Their rarity is counterbalanced by unique skills and potential.
mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_translated: Solicita o contrata la ayuda de Señores y Héroes para tu facción. Su rareza se ve contrarrestada por habilidades y potencial únicos.

mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_original: Recruit emerging companies that have acquired fame in recent exploits.||Once unlocked, these units can be recruited like Regiments of Renown.||Note: these units originate from player stories and are informally known as Regiments of Community.
mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_translated: Recluta compañías emergentes que hayan adquirido fama en hazañas recientes.||Una vez desbloqueadas, estas unidades pueden ser reclutadas como Regimientos de Renombre.|Nota: estas unidades tienen su origen en historias de jugadores y se conocen informalmente como Regimientos de Comunidad.

mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_original: Use your economical, military and political leverage to enact maneuvres and start initiatives.||Each type of Strategy will also lock analogous initiatives for the duration.||For maximum efficiency, timing is of the essence, especially around Great Surge strategies that can only be enacted once each!
mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_translated: Utiliza tu influencia económica, militar y política para llevar a cabo maniobras y poner en marcha iniciativas. Cada tipo de estrategia también bloqueará iniciativas análogas durante el tiempo que dure. Para conseguir la máxima eficacia, el tiempo es esencial, especialmente en las estrategias de Gran Oleada, que sólo pueden llevarse a cabo una vez cada una.

mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_original: Send emissaries to 'acquire' precious items. All items purchased will be added to your Magical Items pool to be equipped by a character from their Character Details panel.||Certain items are expensive to be acquired, one way or another, others are so delightfully unique there is no chance of finding another specimen!
mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_translated: Envía emisarios para "adquirir" objetos preciosos. Todos los objetos comprados se añadirán a tu reserva de objetos mágicos para que los equipe un personaje desde su panel de detalles de personaje. Algunos objetos son caros de adquirir, de una forma u otra, otros son tan deliciosamente únicos que no hay posibilidad de encontrar otro ejemplar.

mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_original: Send emissaries to 'acquire' precious items. All items purchased will be added to your Magical Items pool to be equipped by a character from their Character Details panel.||Certain items are expensive to be acquired, one way or another, others are so delightfully unique there is no chance of finding another specimen!
mortuary_cult_categories_localised_butto.value_translated: Envía emisarios para "adquirir" objetos preciosos. Todos los objetos comprados se añadirán a tu reserva de Objetos Mágicos para que los equipe un personaje desde su panel de Detalles de Personaje. Ciertos objetos son caros de adquirir, de una forma u otra, otros son tan deliciosamente únicos que no hay posibilidad de encontrar otro espécimen.

old___frontend_factions_localised_mechan.value_translated: [[img:bullet_treasury]][[/img]]Plutocracia: una economía fuerte puede mantener grandes gastos, financiar maniobras políticas y alimentar costosas colecciones de objetos exóticos.||[[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Ejércitos mercenarios: versátil y fuertemente blindado elenco de mercenarios locales y extranjeros, que prefieren los Regimientos de Renombre a los complicados artilugios.||[[img:bullet_chs_awaken]][[/img]]La adaptabilidad humana permite crear oportunidades donde otras razas sólo ven adversidades, incluido el dominio de regiones que de otro modo serían inadecuadas.

resources_description_res_location_skave.value_original: This region's climate penalties can be countered by an occupying Southern Realm with great effort.
resources_description_res_location_skave.value_translated: Las penalizaciones climáticas de esta región pueden ser contrarrestadas por un Reino del Sur ocupante con gran esfuerzo.

resources_description_res_location_skv_t.value_original: This location is of special importance to the Skaven and the Southern Realms.
resources_description_res_location_skv_t.value_translated: Esta ubicación es de especial importancia para los Skaven y los Reinos del Sur.

start_pos_factions_description_212013628.value_original: Tilea is a thriving land of arts, trade, visionaries, tyrants, princes, cuisine, mercenaries and, most importantly at this point, divisions. A country born from the ruins of elven colonies, Tilea has never known unity since then, outside of short-lived and individualistic bursts, so that each of the richest and most powerful settlements are in fact autonomous city-states that usually respond quite violently at any external approach of assimilation. It is in a somewhat vicious cycle that tilean warriors are among the best in the Old World, since they are either used to perpetrate the state of division or to otherwise shift huge economical and political assets around.-Cataph
start_pos_factions_description_212013628.value_translated: Tilea es una próspera tierra de artes, comercio, visionarios, tiranos, príncipes, cocina, mercenarios y, lo más importante en este momento, divisiones. País nacido de las ruinas de las colonias élficas, Tilea nunca ha conocido la unidad desde entonces, fuera de efímeros estallidos individualistas, de modo que cada uno de los asentamientos más ricos y poderosos son en realidad ciudades-estado autónomas que suelen responder con bastante violencia a cualquier planteamiento externo de asimilación. Es en un círculo un tanto vicioso donde los guerreros tileanos se encuentran entre los mejores del Viejo Mundo, ya que se utilizan para perpetrar el estado de división o para desplazar de otro modo enormes activos económicos y políticos.-Cataph

start_pos_factions_description_212013629.value_original: Estalia is founded on rivalry. Between Magritta and Bilbali, between the Inquisition and the other powers, with the Tileans, with the Bretonnians, with the Sultans of Araby. If one were to be able to put it on talking terms, perhaps even the Lustrian jungles would agree that, yes, there is a strong rivalry between its unforgiving tendrils and the estalian explorers. However, such relationships can be the base of something extremely wealthy: competition. And upon competition, with the due resources and willpower, a powerful nation can be bred and built, forged in fire and steel, if necessary.-Cataph
start_pos_factions_description_212013629.value_translated: Estalia se basa en la rivalidad. Entre Magritta y Bilbali, entre la Inquisición y las demás potencias, con los tileanos, con los bretonianos, con los sultanes de Araby. Si uno fuera capaz de ponerlo en términos coloquiales, tal vez incluso las junglas lustrianas estarían de acuerdo en que, sí, existe una fuerte rivalidad entre sus implacables zarcillos y los exploradores estalianos. Sin embargo, tales relaciones pueden ser la base de algo extremadamente rico: la competencia. Y sobre la competencia, con los debidos recursos y fuerza de voluntad, se puede criar y construir una nación poderosa, forjada en fuego y acero, si es necesario.-Cataph

start_pos_factions_description_212013630.value_original: Perhaps not a single dweller of the Borderlands would agree to admit it, but the humans of this country are like a large, robust creeper. Centuries ago, human colonists and refugees started to built a new nation on the borders of the Old World. Anyone else would have been strangled between mountain and sea, between Dwarfs and Greenskins. The men of the Borderlands endured the challenge and survive, perhaps in tides and ebbs when the green menace hits harder, but survive nonetheless, without the immense manpower of the Empire, the natural resilience of the Dwarfs, the blessings of the Bretonnians or the wisdom of the High Elves. The men of the Borderlands fight for their hardened pride and their homes.-Cataph
start_pos_factions_description_212013630.value_translated: Puede que ningún habitante de las Tierras Fronterizas esté de acuerdo en admitirlo, pero los humanos de este país son como una enredadera grande y robusta. Hace siglos, colonos y refugiados humanos empezaron a construir una nueva nación en las fronteras del Viejo Mundo. Cualquier otro habría quedado estrangulado entre la montaña y el mar, entre los Enanos y los Pieles Verdes. Los hombres de las Tierras Fronterizas soportaron el desafío y sobreviven, quizá en mareas y reflujos cuando la amenaza verde golpea con más fuerza, pero sobreviven al fin y al cabo, sin la inmensa mano de obra del Imperio, la resistencia natural de los Enanos, las bendiciones de los Bretonianos o la sabiduría de los Altos Elfos. Los hombres de las Tierras Fronterizas luchan por su curtido orgullo y por sus hogares.-Cataph

En el extranjero: Saludos del Imperio

En el extranjero: Cazadores de Bestias

technologies_onscreen_name_teb_pools_tob.value_translated: En el extranjero: Abajo a la Tierra

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: The Borderlands have been Errantry War grounds for the Bretonnians. The bolsterous knights can definitely have uses if their wedges were pointed in the right direction.
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: Las Tierras Fronterizas han sido terreno de Guerra de Errantes para los Bretonianos. Los caballeros fornidos definitivamente pueden tener usos si sus cuñas apuntaran en la dirección correcta.

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: Elector Counts can be persuaded to send a few regiments upon guarantees of protecting the southern borders for them, or to be conniving with their own politicking. Otherwise, you can always find a captain willing to volunteer for profit...
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: Se puede persuadir a los Condes Electores para que envíen algunos regimientos con garantías de proteger las fronteras del sur para ellos, o para que sean conniventes con su propia politiquería. Si no, siempre se puede encontrar un capitán dispuesto a ofrecerse como voluntario...

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: "What do you mean you can't find troops? Look around, there's mercs everywhere! We're swimming in the buggers! You can't bloody walk around without sauntering into those wine-breaths!"
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: "¿Qué quieres decir con que no puedes encontrar tropas? Mira a tu alrededor, ¡hay mercenarios por todas partes! ¡Estamos nadando entre esos cabrones! No puedes caminar sin toparte con esos alientos de vino".

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: We shouldn't let the imperial orders get ideas of independence. They were born here, they will return here. And know who's in charge.
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: No debemos dejar que las órdenes imperiales tengan ideas de independencia. Nacieron aquí, volverán aquí. Y sabrán quién está a cargo.

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: Their attempt at a lustrian foothold didn't go particularly well, but just wave a few challenges and glories at a group of Bretonnians and you might soon have a lance with you.
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: Su intento de afianzarse en el lustro no salió especialmente bien, pero basta con agitar unos cuantos retos y glorias ante un grupo de bretonianos para que pronto puedas tener una lanza contigo.

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: With a few favours, the imperial expedition will certainly share some of their resources. We're all on the same side, aren't we?
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: Con algunos favores, la expedición imperial seguramente compartirá algunos de sus recursos. Todos estamos del mismo lado, ¿no?

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: Anybody can wash up in Tilea as a mercenary, and anybody with a talent for warfare can be put to use.
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: Cualquiera puede llegar a Tilea como mercenario, y cualquiera con talento para la guerra puede ser utilizado.

technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_original: There may be an infinite resource in Tobaro and that is Ratmen in the deeps. Expanding the Deepwatch by using the tunnels as merciless training ground is exactly what Prince Piggalo would have done! Maybe.
technologies_short_description_teb_pools.value_translated: Puede que haya un recurso infinito en Tobaro y son los Hombres Rata de las profundidades. Expandir la Deepwatch usando los túneles como campo de entrenamiento despiadado es exactamente lo que el Príncipe Piggalo habría hecho. Tal vez.

technologies_short_description_teb_tank_.value_original: If one could stack Leonardo da Miragliano's sketches in a pile, they'd probably reach Morrslieb. Upstart polymath Ugoletti has expressed interest in trying to make sense in one of these, so far kept secret. A wooden vehicle of bizarre shape, but the crank design looks all wrong...
technologies_short_description_teb_tank_.value_translated: Si se pudieran apilar los bocetos de Leonardo da Miragliano, probablemente llegarían hasta Morrslieb. El advenedizo polímata Ugoletti ha expresado su interés por intentar dar sentido a uno de ellos, hasta ahora mantenido en secreto. Un vehículo de madera de forma extraña, pero el diseño de la manivela parece totalmente erróneo...

technologies_short_description_teb_tank_.value_original: The prototype seems to be somewhat working after bypassing Leonardo's puzzles, but Ugoletti needs more funding to improve the construction process and design. Your treasurers are murmuring.
technologies_short_description_teb_tank_.value_translated: El prototipo parece funcionar algo tras sortear los rompecabezas de Leonardo, pero Ugoletti necesita más fondos para mejorar el proceso de construcción y el diseño. Sus tesoreros murmuran.

technologies_short_description_teb_tank_.value_original: Ugoletti claims that he can perfect the design, if only he could get his hands on an efficient power source; however, his sauce-splattered notes are exceedingly nebulous and he seems to be falling prey to hyperactive paranoia. If only one would fund an expedition to the jungles, for one of those things he calls Solar Engines...
technologies_short_description_teb_tank_.value_translated: Ugoletti afirma que puede perfeccionar el diseño, si tan sólo pudiera hacerse con una fuente de energía eficiente; sin embargo, sus notas salpicadas de salsa son excesivamente nebulosas y parece estar cayendo presa de una paranoia hiperactiva. Si tan sólo se financiara una expedición a las selvas, en busca de una de esas cosas que él llama Motores Solares...

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: When the conditions and prospects of profit are right, even the expense behind recruiting and convincing the very best mercenaries in the Southern Realms can be justified...
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Cuando las condiciones y las perspectivas de beneficio son las adecuadas, incluso el gasto que supone reclutar y convencer a los mejores mercenarios de los Reinos del Sur puede estar justificado...

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Even as far as the New World, famous mercenaries can be persuaded to come, or even found locally.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Incluso hasta el Nuevo Mundo, se puede convencer a mercenarios famosos para que vengan, o incluso encontrarlos localmente.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Most Condottieri won't leave home without a company or two of toughened veterans. Others will want a jewel to their hat in the way of a famous regiment.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: La mayoría de los Condottieri no saldrán de casa sin una o dos compañías de curtidos veteranos. Otros querrán una joya en su sombrero en forma de regimiento famoso.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: The jungle polishes the refugees, the brigands, the generic scallywags and even the honest (until proven otherwise) entrepreneurs into shrewd tough nuts. Or merciless despoilers.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: La jungla pule a los refugiados, a los bandidos, a los bribones genéricos e incluso a los honrados (hasta que se demuestre lo contrario) empresarios para convertirlos en astutos chiflados. O despiadados saqueadores.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: The Border Confederacy is far from alien to aggressions. Countless greenskin and beastmen invasions tried to break them, unsuccessfully.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: La Confederación Fronteriza no es ajena a las agresiones. Innumerables invasiones de pielesverdes y hombres bestia intentaron doblegarlos, sin éxito.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Following the unmistakable act of throwing crates of imported pasta (and the former Viceroy) in the harbour's waters, the thriving colonies start a new adventure entirely of their own.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Tras el inconfundible acto de arrojar cajas de pasta importada (y al antiguo Virrey) a las aguas del puerto, las prósperas colonias inician una nueva aventura totalmente propia.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: "See here, we have to form up the troops into curved arrows and drive them deep into the enemy oblongs. What? Diagrams are clear."
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: "Mira aquí, tenemos que formar las tropas en flechas curvas y clavarlas profundamente en los oblongos enemigos. ¿Qué? Los diagramas son claros".

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: These soldiers may appear out of touch and out of the loop with modern warfare, but they're far from ineffective.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Estos soldados pueden parecer ajenos a la guerra moderna, pero están lejos de ser ineficaces.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Those that come back from Lustria have plenty to tell about exotic beasts, incredible treasures and amazing scars. And know how to kill and plunder quickly and efficiently.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Los que vuelven de Lustria tienen mucho que contar sobre bestias exóticas, tesoros increíbles y cicatrices asombrosas. Y saben matar y saquear con rapidez y eficacia.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Elves and Lizards don't know all monsters, and Man is one that is relentless.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Los Elfos y los Lagartos no conocen a todos los monstruos, y el Hombre es uno que es implacable.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: "Keep 'em payments to the little buggers regular and they won't raze your city to the ground because you filed a couple of coins. Oh, Master Dwarf, what a lovely surprise!"
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: "Mantén los pagos a los pequeños bichos regulares y no arrasarán tu ciudad porque hayas limado un par de monedas. Oh, Maese Enano, ¡qué sorpresa tan encantadora!"

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Inspired by the fabled might of Tylos, by the elven legacy and driven by the pent-up potential in the wealthy Tilea of nowadays, one might think of ways to overcome the usual tilean rivalry for something greater...
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Inspirado por el legendario poder de Tylos, por el legado de los elfos e impulsado por el potencial reprimido en la rica Tilea de hoy en día, uno podría pensar en formas de superar la habitual rivalidad tileana para conseguir algo más grande...

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: A soldier that has faced many a defeat is less likely to just run away at the first sign of trouble.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Un soldado que se ha enfrentado a muchas derrotas es menos propenso a huir a la primera señal de problemas.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: It's only natural for the South to invest money (albeit begrudgingly) in garrisons, considering the average neighbour is a scheming prince or a greenskin warband.
"You think that's scary? Wake me up when it starts spitting fire all over the pl-Alright, alright, bloody Myrmidia, I'm coming."
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: "¿Crees que da miedo? Despiértame cuando empiece a escupir fuego por todas partes. Muy bien, muy bien, maldita Myrmidia, ya voy".

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: The inquisitorial Tribunals have little patience for petty concepts such as 'mercy', 'proof' and 'innocence'.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Los Tribunales inquisitoriales tienen poca paciencia para conceptos mezquinos como "piedad", "prueba" e "inocencia".

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: When you are the one holding the lit candle for the surgeon to amputate your own leg, you got your troops full respect until the day you die.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Cuando eres tú quien sostiene la vela encendida para que el cirujano te ampute tu propia pierna, tienes a tus tropas todo el respeto hasta el día de tu muerte.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Actual war is only the last resort in the art of diplomacy, and leverage is just another kind of artillery.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: La guerra real es sólo el último recurso en el arte de la diplomacia, y el apalancamiento no es más que otro tipo de artillería.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Mercenaries know how to make their risky lives a little bit more sustainable. Surely not for the others.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Los mercenarios saben cómo hacer que sus arriesgadas vidas sean un poco más sostenibles. Seguro que no para los demás.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: The highlanders of the Irrana Mountains are renowned for their odd drinks and effective skirmishers.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Los montañeses de las Montañas Irrana son famosos por sus extrañas bebidas y sus eficaces escaramuzadores.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: The Cult of Myrmidia abhors Chaos in all its forms, and when it draws near, the Order of the Eagle must take arms.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: El Culto de Myrmidia aborrece el Caos en todas sus formas, y cuando se acerca, la Orden del Águila debe tomar las armas.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: We need to encourage the building of new chapterhouses in our territories if we want the support of the Myrmidian Orders, who so far considered the Border Princes not quite important enough. They weren't wrong, mind you.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Debemos fomentar la construcción de nuevas salas capitulares en nuestros territorios si queremos contar con el apoyo de las Órdenes mirmidianas, que hasta ahora consideraban que los Príncipes de la Frontera no eran lo bastante importantes. No se equivocaban, eso sí.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: The New World is a shrine of dangers and secrets, expensive ones. The most common trinket a bait to destruction or an unthinkable tool of power.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: El Nuevo Mundo es un santuario de peligros y secretos, de los caros. La baratija más común un cebo para la destrucción o una impensable herramienta de poder.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: After years of hardship, the Borderlands can finally prosper, their fighters defending not fearful towns but proud capitals.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Tras años de penurias, las Tierras Fronterizas por fin pueden prosperar, sus combatientes no defienden pueblos temerosos, sino orgullosas capitales.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: "See the scruffy one with the bandage and the limp? Pick that one. Just do it."
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: "¿Ves al desaliñado con el vendaje y la cojera? Elige a ese. Hazlo".

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Many are the tales of those lone riders, the somewhat-anti-heroes who head into the deep countryside to exact some sort of justice. Steel-eyed and quick-firing, often announced by the music of a carillon.
"Nothing but tha best armour here-a! Quarrel tested! Money back guaranteed if it breaks!"
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: "¡Sólo las mejores armaduras! ¡Probada en combate! ¡Devolución del dinero garantizada si se rompe!"

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: By the union of impenetrable pike formations, daring cavalry actions and, of course, substantial economical support, Tilean warfare can reign supreme.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Mediante la unión de impenetrables formaciones de picas, audaces acciones de caballería y, por supuesto, un sustancial apoyo económico, la guerra tileana puede reinar suprema.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: In a heterogeneous mercenary army, coordination is key to victory. And a well-cooperating host is like an unstoppable grinder.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: En un ejército mercenario heterogéneo, la coordinación es clave para la victoria. Y una hueste bien coordinada es como una trituradora imparable.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: By superior training - if not superior looks - the tercio can melt away any opposition by sheer efficiency of combined arms.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Gracias a un entrenamiento superior -si no a un aspecto superior-, el tercio puede acabar con cualquier oposición mediante la pura eficacia de los brazos combinados.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: It can't be ignored - Tilea is the land of art, wealth and continuous warfare. Tilean mercenaries are highly valued for reasons beyond their funny accent.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: No se puede ignorar: Tilea es la tierra del arte, la riqueza y la guerra continua. Los mercenarios tileanos son muy apreciados por razones que van más allá de su gracioso acento.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: The wealth of the Southern Realms flows through sea and land, into chests and pockets, and back again.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: La riqueza de los Reinos del Sur fluye por mar y tierra, a cofres y bolsillos, y de vuelta.

technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_original: Devoid of flashy armour and banners of more famed regiments, the hardened border scouts fight a humble and endless struggle of their own.
technologies_short_description_teb_tech_.value_translated: Desprovistos de las llamativas armaduras y estandartes de regimientos más afamados, los aguerridos exploradores fronterizos libran una humilde e interminable lucha propia.

ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_original: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Armies of the Borderlands: jack-of-all-trades roster of skirmishers, specialists and cost-effective compromises.
ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_translated: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Ejércitos de las Tierras Fronterizas: un listado de unidades multiusos, como escaramuzadores, especialistas y unidades a precios asequibles.

ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_original: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Colonial Armies: jack-of-all-trades roster that combines many of the individual strengths of the homeland with fewer of their elites.
ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_translated: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Ejércitos coloniales: listado de unidades polifacéticas que combina muchos de los puntos fuertes individuales de la patria con menos de sus élites.

ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_original: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Armies of Estalia: reliable and heavily-armoured roster, with versatile Conquistador units.
ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_translated: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Ejércitos de Estalia: elenco fiable y fuertemente blindado, con versátiles unidades de Conquistadores.

ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_original: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Armies of Tilea: reliable and heavily-armoured roster, with better artillery and cavalry than their neighbours.
ui_text_replacements_localised_text_fron.value_translated: [[img:bullet_armies]][[/img]]Ejércitos de Tilea: elenco fiable y fuertemente blindado, con mejor artillería y caballería que sus vecinos.

ui_text_replacements_localised_text_teb_.value_original: [[img:plutocracy]][[/img]] [[col:white]]Plutocracy[[/col]]\\n[[col:green]]Use your {{tr:icon_treasury}}treasury, when strategically viable, to fund [[img:ui/skins/default/browser_spell_tab_character.png]][[/img]]specific agents or even unique characters, hire special [[img:ui/skins/default/icon_effect_ror.png]][[/img]]Regiments of Renown, purchase [[img:icon_prologue_character]][[/img]]character items, and [[img:ui/skins/default/icon_factions.png]][[/img]]initiate temporary factionwide bonuses. \\n\\nSouthern Realms have few ways of reducing expenses but many to increase income, particularly from ports buildings and province capitals.[[/col]]
ui_text_replacements_localised_text_teb_.value_translated: [[img:plutocracy]][[/img]] [[col:white]]Plutocracia[[/col]]\\n[[col:green]]Utiliza tu {{tr:icon_treasury}}tesoro, cuando sea estratégicamente viable, para financiar [[img:ui/skins/default/browser_spell_tab_character.png]][[/img]]agentes específicos o incluso personajes únicos, contratar [[img:ui/skins/default/icon_effect_ror.png]][[/img]]Regimientos de Renombre especiales, comprar [[img:icon_prologue_character]][[/img]]objetos de personajes, e iniciar [[img:ui/skins/default/icon_factions.png]][[/img]]bonificaciones temporales para toda la facción. \\n\\nLos Reinos del Sur tienen pocas formas de reducir los gastos, pero muchas de aumentar los ingresos, sobre todo de los edificios portuarios y las capitales de provincia.[[/col]]
